0Lending%20Rate%20Unchanged%20At%206.5%25%20For%20Third%20Time%20In%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20bank%20of%20the%20country%20today%20kept%20the%20key%20lending%20rate%20unchanged%20at%206.5%25%20for%20the%20third%20time%20in%20a%20row%2C%20but%20said%20inflation%20rates%20are%20likely%20to%20rise%20led%20by%20vegetable%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee%20has%20unanimously%20decided%20to%20keep%20the%20policy%20repo%20rate%20unchanged.%20This%20means%20the%20loan%20interest%20rates%20too%20are%20likely%20to%20remain%20unchanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20economy%20is%20exuding%20enhanced%20strength%20and%20stability%20despite%20global%20shocks%2C%20said%20the%20Governor%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20contributing%2015%25%20to%20global%20growth.%20The%20country%20is%20uniquely%20placed%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20ongoing%20transformational%20shifts%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20raised%20the%20inflation%20forecast%20for%20the%20current%20financial%20year%20from%205.1%25%20to%205.4%25%2C%20citing%20rising%20vegetable%20prices.%20The%20inflation%20rate%20shot%20up%20from%204.3%25%20in%20May%20to%204.8%25%20in%20June%2C%20with%20the%20figure%20expected%20to%20rise%20further%20in%20July%20and%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20spike%20in%20tomato%20prices%20led%20to%20accentuating%20food%20inflation%20in%20July%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Governor%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20price%20rise%20was%20short-term%20and%20it%20will%20reduce%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Das%20said%20the%20cumulative%20rate%20hikes%20taken%20so%20far%20are%20working%20their%20way%20into%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20developments%20require%20heightened%20vigil%20on%20the%20evolving%20inflation%20trajectory%2C%20said%20Mr%20Das%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20domestic%20economic%20activity%20is%20holding%20