20Rahul%20Gandhi%20just%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsmritiirani%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40smritiirani%3C%2Fa%3E%20spoke.%20Is%20there%20any%20other%20video%20of%20him%20allegedly%20blowing%20%E2%80%9CFlying%20Kiss%E2%80%9D%20to%20Smriti%20Irani%20as%20claimed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShobhaBJP%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ShobhaBJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3Cbr%3EAlso%20in%20her%2C%20speech%20Smriti%20Irani%20said%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20blew%20a%20%E2%80%98flying%20kiss%E2%80%99%20to%20a%20Parliament%20which%20has%20female%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcZJl5X3QaQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcZJl5X3QaQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mohammed%20Zubair%20(%40zoo_bear)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzoo_bear%2Fstatus%2F1689196941094367232%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20we%20have%20seen%20such%20behaviour%20from%20an%20MP%20in%20the%20House.%20He%20made%20a%20gesture%20of%20a%20flying%20kiss%20at%20women%20MPs%20in%20the%20House%E2%80%A6It%20is%20unacceptable.%20We%20have%20complained%20to%20the%20Speaker%20to%20take%20action%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Union%20minister%20Shobha%20Karandlaje%20outside%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20letter%20has%20also%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1689200241411780608%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1689200241411780608%257Ctwgr%255E92b84b57b9370f775b9bb82bb76ef56c44195805%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Findianexpress.com%252Farticle%252Findia%252Frahul-gandhis-flying-kiss-triggers-row-bjp-calls-it-misogynistic-behaviour-congress-says-side-tracking-strategy-8883976%252F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eposted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Tw