%20the%20people%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20hate%20us%20by%20telling%20us%20about%20tourism%20and%20development.It%20is%20not%20tourism%20and%20development%20but%20love%20that%20you%20have%20to%20give..%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20had%20G20%20meetings%20and%20you%20said%20to%20the%20whole%20world%20what%20a%20great%20tourism%20meeting%20you%20had%20but%20you%20could%20not%20take%20them%20to%20Gulmarg%2C%20Dachigam.%20Because%20you%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20say%20there%20is%20no%20terrorism%20there..Look%20at%C2%A0%20Rajouri%2C%20Kulgam..See%20how%20our%20neighbour%20is%20behaving.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20say%20to%20this%20government%20and%20to%20the%20people%20of%20india-remember%20what%20Vajpayee%20said%2C%20you%20can%20change%20friends%20but%20not%20neighbours.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoS%20home%20Nityananda%20Rai%20then%20rose%20from%20his%20seat%20and%20countered%20Abdullah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20India%20is%20so%20strong%20no%20neighbour%20dares%20to%20fight.%20India%20is%20proud%20of%20its%20government%20and%20its%20PM.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20V.K.%20Singh%20also%20countered%20Abdullah%20about%20why%20the%20plebiscite%20was%20not%20held.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20plebiscite%20did%20not%20happen%20because%20there%20was%20a%20condition%20that%20Pakistan%20would%20remove%20troops%20from%20POK.%20Let%20us%20not%20talk%20about%20plebiscites%20not%20being%20held.%20The%20condition%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20fulfilled%2C%20the%20plebiscite%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20held%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691641717000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10095555%2FUntitled-design-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fth