umed%20its%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20showed%20aerosol%20particles%20inside%20the%20coach%20and%20a%20shattered%20window%2C%20apparently%20a%20result%20of%20panic%20among%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20unauthorised%20passenger%20boarded%20the%20train%20from%20Tirupati%20and%20locked%20himself%20in%20the%20toilet%20of%20the%20C-13%20coach.%20He%20smoked%20inside%20the%20toilet%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20automatic%20activation%20of%20an%20aerosol%20fire%20extinguisher%20inside%20the%20toilet%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20from%20South%20Central%20Railway%20(SCR)%20Zone's%20Vijayawada%20Division%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691641380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fp9lcd3u_vande-bharat_625x300_10_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvande-bharat-express-man-travelling-ticketless-on-vande-bharat-lights-cigarette-this-happens-4285130%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20is%20in%20news%20again%2C%20not%20for%20stone%20attacks%20or%20collisions%20with%20cattle%2C%20but%20for%20a%20ticketless%20passenger%20who%20could%20not%20resist%20the%20craving%20for%20a%20cigarette%20during%20the%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvande-bharat-express-man-travelling-ticketless-on-vande-bharat-lights-cigarette-this-happens-4285130%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvande-bharat-express-man-travelling-ticketless-on-vande-bharat-lights-cigarette-this-happens-4285130%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvande-bharat-express-man-travelling-ticketless-on-vande-bharat-lights-cigarette-this-happens-4285130%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22German%20official%20accused%20of%20spying%20for%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22pu