2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20the%20legislature%20cannot%20stop%20enacting%20laws%20nor%20judiciary%20can%20stop%20applying%20them%20only%20because%20they%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Bmisused%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20are%20enacted%20to%20curb%20offences%20and%20get%20justice%20to%20genuine%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20contentions%20of%20learned%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioner%20in%20the%20pleadings%20as%20well%20as%20during%20oral%20arguments%20that%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20is%20a%20gender%20based%20legislation%20and%20therefore%20is%20being%20misused%20is%20not%20only%20inappropriate%20but%20misleading%20too.%20To%20say%20the%20least%2C%20POCSO%20Act%20is%20not%20gender%20based%20and%20is%20neutral%20as%20far%20as%20victim%20children%20are%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20court%20in%20a%20recent%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20law%2C%20whether%20gender%20based%20or%20not%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20of%20being%20misused.%20However%2C%20only%20because%20laws%20can%20be%20misused%2C%20the%20legislature%20cannot%20stop%20enacting%20laws%20nor%20judiciary%20can%20stop%20applying%20such%20laws%20since%20they%20have%20been%20enacted%20to%20curb%20the%20larger%20menace%20of%20commission%20of%20such%20offences%20and%20getting%20justice%20to%20genuine%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20refused%20to%20direct%20re-cross%20examination%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20who%20was%20seven%20years%20old%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%20in%202016%2C%20as%20well%20as%20her%20mother%20before%20the%20trial%20court%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20duty%20bound%20to%20remain%20sensitive%20to%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20minor%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20and%20her%20mother%2C%20the%20court%20opined%2C%20cannot%20be%20recalled%20to%20relive%20the%20entire%20trauma%20after%20six%20years%20of%20conclusion%20of%20their%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20perusal%20of%20the%20record%20would%20reveal%20that%20six%20years%20have%20passed%20since%20the%20testimonies%20of%20the%20prosecutrix%20and%20her%20mother%20were%20recorded%20before%20the%20learned%20Trial%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20Court%20cannot%20dispute%20that%20the%20right%20to%20fair%20trial%20is%20a%20crucial%20and%20precious%20right%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20so%20is%20the%20complainant's%20right%20to%20a%20fair%20trial%20which%20requires%20that%20they%20should%20not%20unnecessarily%20be%20harassed%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691639580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Ft72t3c1g_delhi-high-court-650_625x300_11_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpocso-act-a-gender-neutral-legislation-says-delhi-high-court-4283458%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20is%20a%20gender-neutral%20legislation%20while%20rejecting%20an%20assertion%20that%20the%20law%20is%20being%20%26quot%3Bmisused%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgender%20based%26quot%3B%20enactment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpocso-act-a-gender-neutral-legislation-says-delhi-high-court-4283458%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpocso-act-a-gender-neutral-legislation-says-delhi-high-court-4283458%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpocso-act-a-gender-neutral-legislation-says-delhi-high-court-4283458%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IND%20vs%20WI%3A%20Manjrekar%20Picks%20Real%20Match