riants%20in%20his%20lab%20at%20Columbia%20University%20to%20see%20how%20resistant%20they%20have%20become%20to%20the%20antibodies%20we%20have%20to%20defend%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHo%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20CNN%3A%20%26quot%3BBoth%20are%20only%20slightly%20more%20resistant%20to%20neutralizing%20antibodies%20in%20the%20serum%20of%20infected%20and%20vaccinated%20persons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClinically%2C%20he%20said%2C%20these%20variants%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20causing%20different%20or%20more%20severe%20symptoms%20than%20the%20viruses%20that%20came%20before%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20basically%20has%20some%20more%20immune%20escape%20compared%20to%20the%20ones%20that%20were%20precedents%20in%20this%20XBB%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Eric%20Topol%2C%20a%20cardiologist%20at%20the%20Scripps%20Translational%20Research%20Institute.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20an%20advantage%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it's%20getting%20legs%20all%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEG.5%20is%20also%20growing%20quickly%20in%20Ireland%2C%20France%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Japan%20and%20China.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organization%20on%20Wednesday%20upgraded%20its%20status%20from%20a%20variant%20under%20monitoring%20to%20a%20variant%20of%20interest%2C%20a%20move%20that%20signals%20the%20agency%20thinks%20it%20should%20be%20tracked%20and%20studied%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691639460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2Fn10s65dg_omicron-covid-us-afp_625x300_06_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-covid-variant-eg-5-causing-17-cases-in-us-report-4285034%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20COVID-19%20variant%20EG.5%20is%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20US%20and%20is%20causing