7%20wickets%20at%20the%20Providence%20Stadium%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20important%20to%20win.%20We%20spoke%20as%20a%20group%20that%20these%20three%20games%20will%20be%20exciting.%20Two%20losses%20or%20two%20wins%20does%20not%20change%20the%20long-term%20plans.%20We%20have%20to%20show%20we%20are%20ready%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20such%20(must-win)%20games.%20Nicky%20(Nicholas%20Pooran)%20did%20not%20come%20out%20to%20bat%20and%20that%20allowed%20us%20to%20keep%20our%20pacers%20back%2C%20and%20also%20allowed%20Axar%20to%20bowl%20his%20four%20overs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hardik%20in%20a%20post-match%20presentation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Nicky%20wants%20to%20hit%2C%20let%20him%20hit%20me%20and%20that%20was%20the%20plan%2C%20I%20enjoy%20such%20competition.%20I%20know%20he%20is%20going%20to%20hear%20this%20and%20will%20come%20hard%20at%20me%20in%20the%20fourth%20T20I.%20As%20a%20group%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20bat%20with%20seven%20batters%20and%20we%20have%20to%20take%20responsibility%2C%20like%20it%20happened%20today%20if%20the%20batters%20score%20runs%20then%20you%20don't%20need%20someone%20at%20number%20eight.%20As%20Surya%20mentioned%2C%20they%20(Suryakumar%20and%20Tilak)%20play%20together%20and%20spend%20time%20together%2C%20good%20to%20have%20someone%20like%20Surya%20in%20the%20team%20and%20when%20he%20takes%20responsibility%20it%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20the%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Hardik.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20win%2C%20India%20has%20managed%20to%20keep%20the%20series%20alive%20by%202-1.%20There%20are%20two%20more%20games%20to%20go.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691636640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ff1bi8he_hardik-pandya-mukesh-kumar-afp_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ftwo-losses-wont-change-hardik-pandya-defiant-over-long-term-plans-4281723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20the%20Indian%20team's%20'long-term'%20plans%20remained%20intact%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20T20I%20side%20had%20lost%20the%20first%20two%20matches%20of%20the%20series%20against%20West%20Indies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ftwo-losses-wont-change-hardik-pandya-defiant-over-long-term-plans-4281723%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ftwo-losses-wont-change-hardik-pandya-defiant-over-long-term-plans-4281723%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ftwo-losses-wont-change-hardik-pandya-defiant-over-long-term-plans-4281723%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%203%20Of%20No-Trust%20Debate%20In%20Parliament%2C%20PM's%20Reply%20Today%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20parliament%20witnessed%20a%20fierce%20debate%20last%20two%20days%20with%20the%20Opposition%20accusing%20the%20government%20of%20creating%20a%20great%20divide%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20government%20has%20defended%20its%20actions%2C%20focusing%20primarily%20on%20its%20welfare%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAddressing%20the%20parliament%20yesterday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20questioned%20why%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20not%20visited%20Manipur%20yet.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20not%20gone%20to%20Manipur%20because%20he%20doesn't%20consider%20it%20a%20part%20of%20India.%20You%20(BJP)%20have%20divided%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20amid%20loud%20protests%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20presented%20a%20report%20card%20of%20the%20centre%20in%20terms%20of%20fighting%20Covid%20and%20the%20drugs%20menace.%20He%20also%20clarified%20the%20government's%20efforts%20in%20addressing%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20and%20alleged%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20brought%20to%20%26quot%3Bmislead%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20has%20confirmed%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20be%20present%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Thursday%20to%20reply%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion.%20The%20Opposition%20had%20been%20demanding%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20in%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20centre%20earlier%20agreed%20to%20take%20up%20discussions%20related%20to%20Manipur%20violence%20on%20August%2011%2C%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20Monsoon%20Session.%20But%20the%20date%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20which%20has%20331%20members%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20sail%20through%20the%20no-trust%20vote.%20The%20BJP%20alone%20has%20303%20MPs%20in%20the%20Lower%20House%20where%20the%20majority%20mark%20is%20272.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20144%20MPs%20and%20its%20tally%20can%20go%20up%20to%20152%20if%20it%20can%20win%20the%20nine%20votes%20of%20the%20BRS.%20Besides%2C%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%20YSRCP%20and%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20BJD%20have%2070%20members%20together.%20BJD%20is%20not%20backing%20the%20no-trust%20motion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20discussion%20on%20Manipur%2C%20but%20the%20government%20had%20asserted%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20not%20address%20the%20House%20on%20the%20issue.%20The%20opposition%20argue%20that%20the%20no-trust%20motion%20will%20help%20them%20win%20the%20%26quot%3Bbattle%20of%20perception%26quot%3B%20by%20cornering%20the%20government%20and%20compel%20the%20PM%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20a%20strategic%20parliamentary%20tool%20that%20the%20opposition%20can%20use%20to%20express%20its%20lack%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20government.%20It%20compels%20the%20ruling%20party%20or%20alliance%20to%20prove%20its%20majority%20in%20the%20House.%20If%20it%20loses%20majority%2C%20the%20government%20falls%20immediately.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20no-confidence%20motions%20have%20been%20moved%2027%20times%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20but%20all%20of%20them%20were%20either%20defeated%20or%20remained%20inconclusive.%20But%20governments%20have%20fallen%20at%20least%20thrice%20during%20vote%20of%20motion%20of%20confidence%2C%20which%20is%20moved%20by%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20to%20prove%20its%20strength.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691636580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Famts2j3g_pm-modi-in-lok-sabha-pti-650_650x400_08_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-reply-to-no-confidence-motion-in-lok-sabha-today-10-points-4284962%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20today%20reply%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20brought%20by%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20corner%20the%20government%20over%20the%20violence%20raging%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-reply-to-no-confidence-motion-in-lok-sabha-today-10-points-4284962%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-reply-to-no-confidence-motion-in-lok-sabha-today-10-points-4284962%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-reply-to-no-confidence-motion-in-lok-sabha-today-10-points-4284962%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Goodb