hen.%20Congratulations%20to%20the%20Lionesses%20of%20the%20Atlas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBenzina%2C%20too%2C%20offered%20yet%20more%20recognition%20for%20athletes%20and%20young%20girls%20who%20wear%20hijabs%2C%20as%20the%2025-year-old%20was%20recently%20added%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20football%20video%20game%2C%20EA%E2%80%99s%20FIFA%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20lot%20of%20people%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20disrespect%20on%20African%20nations%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expectations%20for%20and%20around%20Nigeria%20were%20heightened%20given%20the%20Super%20Falcons%20have%20played%20in%20all%20nine%20editions%20of%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20lead-up%20to%20the%20competition%20was%20ruined%20when%20their%20training%20camp%20in%20Nigeria%20was%20cancelled%20and%20uncertainty%20reigned%20over%20whether%20they%20would%20be%20paid%20%E2%80%93%20with%20allegations%20that%20they%20had%20failed%20to%20be%20remunerated%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20FIFA%20having%20announced%20that%20each%20player%C2%A0reaching%20the%20Round%20of%2016%20would%20receive%20a%20minimum%20of%20US%20%2450%2C000%20(%E2%82%AC45.600)%2C%C2%A0forward%20Uchenna%20Kanu%20admitted%20to%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20she%20was%20unsure%20if%20the%20Nigeria%20Football%20Federation%20(NFA)%20would%20pass%20that%20money%20on%20to%20the%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20their%20off-field%20battles%20remained%20a%20topic%20of%20discussion%20throughout%20the%20tournament%2C%20the%20team%20produced%20some%20of%20the%20best-attacking%20football%20of%20the%20group%20stages%2C%20as%20their%20quick%20counter-attacks%20and%20bravery%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwomens-world-cup-nigeria%2Fa-66369688%5C%22%3Ehelped%20them%20beat%20hosts%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20own%20Round%20of%2016%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-cup-ten-woman-england-survive-super-falcons-scare%2Fa-66457197%5C%22%3Edemise%20against%20European%20champions%20England%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20penalties%20was%20harsh%2C%20given%20the%20African%20side%20had%20shaded%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20120%20minutes%20of%20open%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-cup-ashleigh-plumptre-nigeria%2Fa-66185830%5C%22%3Edefender%20Ashleigh%20Pumptre%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20team%E2%80%99s%20play%20finally%20showed%20the%20world%20that%20African%20sides%20are%20capable%20of%20more%20than%20just%20using%20their%20%E2%80%9Cstrength.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20disrespect%20on%20African%20nations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explained%20to%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20say%20they%E2%80%99re%20just%20physical%20or%20they%E2%80%99re%20just%20fast%2C%20but%20you%20can%20see%20we%20have%20incredibly%20technical%20players%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20now%20more%20people%20need%20to%20be%20talking%20about%20what%20we%20do%20as%20an%20overall%20footballing%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20like%20a%20kick%20and%20run%2C%20and%20people%20do%20make%20those%20kinds%20of%20assumptions.%20It%E2%80%99s%20nice%20that%20all%20African%20teams%20at%20this%20tournament%20have%20showcased%20what%20they%E2%80%99re%20all%20about.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDomestic%20South%20African%20league%20deserves%20immediate%20investment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20moment%20of%20reckoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELacking%20World%20Cup%20contracts%2C%20a%20resolution%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20for%20Banyana%20Banyana%C2%A0as%20the%20side%20is%20known%2C%20until%C2%A0billionaire%20Patrice%20Motsepe%20%E2%80%94%20owner%20of%C2%A0the%20South%20African%20professional%20team%C2%A0Mamelodi%20Sundowns%20and%C2%A0president%20of%20the%20Confederation%20of%20African%20Football%C2%A0%E2%80%94%C2%A0intervened%20and%20made%20a%20%24320%2C000%C2%A0donation%20to%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audacity%20of%20asking%C2%A0for%20recompense%20did%20not%20go%20down%20well%20with%20many%20in%20South%20Africa%C2%A0and%C2%A0after%20the%20team%20let%20a%20two-goal%20lead%20slip%20during%20their%20group%20match%20against%20Argentina%C2%A0they%20were%20bombarded%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20sensational%20last-minute%20winner%20from%20stand-in%20captain%20and%20winning%20goalscorer%20Thembi%20Kgatlana%20propelled%20South%20Africa%20to%20the%20knockout%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kgatlana%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20lost%20three%20family%20members%20in%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%20and%20I%20could%20have%20gone%20home%2C%20but%20this%20was%20too%20important.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20team%20departed%20at%20the%20Round%20of%2016%20after%20losing%20to%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20head%20coach%20Desiree%20Ellis%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-cup-south-africas-success-deserves-off-field-support%2Fa-66455722%5C%22%3Eissued%20the%20following%20rallying%20cry%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CTo%20the%20sponsors%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20you%20can%20ignore%20something%20special%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20assist%20in%20getting%20us%20to%20climb%20the%20ladder.%20We%20still%20have%20players%20who%20have%20a%209-to-5%20job%20and%20then%20go%20to%20train%20in%20the%20evening.%20That%E2%80%99s%20unacceptable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECross%20country%20support%20key%20for%20African%20nations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zambia%2C%20there%20was%20no%20fairy%20tale%20ending%2C%20but%20they%20did%20secure%20their%20first-ever%20World%20Cup%20victory%20when%20they%20swatted%20aside%20Costa%20Rica%20in%20their%20final%20group%20match%20in%20Hamilton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20reports%20emerged%20that%20coach%20Bruce%20Mwape%20has%20been%20under%20investigation%20by%20FIFA%20over%20sexual%20abuse%20claims%20from%20his%20players%20and%20a%20further%20allegation%20was%20lodged%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20group%20stage%20claiming%C2%A0the%20head%20coach%20had%20inappropriately%20touched%20one%20of%20his%20players%20during%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFans%20from%20various%20African%20countries%20travelled%20to%20both%20Hamilton%20and%20Auckland%20to%20support%20the%20Zambian%20side%20but%20were%20dismayed%20upon%20learning%20of%20the%20accusations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20in%20the%20stands%2C%20like%20Joyce%20Chitepo%2C%20said%20they%20felt%20it%20all%20the%20more%20important%C2%A0to%20be%C2%A0vocal%20and%20vibrant%20in%20their%20encouragement%20for%20the%20players%20in%20light%20of%20such%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20girls%20should%20know%20we%20are%20here%20to%20cheer%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Zimbabwean-born%20Chitepo%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20the%20support%20of%20all%20of%20Africa%2C%20like%20every%20team%20does.%20We%E2%80%99re%20stronger%20when%20we%20support%20each%20other.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fafrican-women-world-cup-2023%2Fa-66470357%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26