2visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10099%2Fproduction%2F_130698656_a0efc29d-2cb2-48b3-8a0f-dfd3e6a73389.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66364272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Victims'%20families%20are%20distraught%20that%20Russian%20prisoners%20released%20to%20fight%20in%20Ukraine%20are%20reoffending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A133%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66364272%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66364272.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66364272.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20May%20Call%20It%20J%26K%20Constitution%20But...%3A%20Court%20During%20Article%20370%20Hearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%2C%20which%20bestowed%20special%20status%20on%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20not%20a%20repository%20of%20untrammelled%20power%20but%20a%20medium%20through%20which%20the%20Constitution%20would%20apply%20to%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20told%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20was%20told%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Gopal%20Subramanium%2C%20appearing%20for%20petitioner%20Muzaffar%20Iqbal%20Khan%2C%20that%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20constituent%20assembly%20did%20not%20want%20to%20abrogate%20Article%20370%20and%20instead%20permitted%20its%20continuance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20has%20challenged%20the%20two%20constitutional%20orders%20of%20the%20Centre%20issued%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%20and%20August%206%2C%202019%2C%20by%20which%20Article%20370%20was%20abrogated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20the%20word%20'temporary'%20appears%20in%20the%20marginal%20notes%20of%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20constituent%20assembly%20said%20that%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20must%20apply%20with%20these%20modifications.%20The%20constitution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Indian%20Constitution%20were%20speaking%20to%20each%20other%20through%20Article%20370%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Subramanium%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20bench%20also%20comprising%20justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%2C%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Surya%20Kant%20that%20Article%20370%20was%20not%20a%20repository%20of%20untrammelled%20power%20but%20a%20medium%20through%20which%20the%20Constitution%20would%20apply%20to%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Subramanium%2C%20who%20commenced%20his%20arguments%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20hearing%20on%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20respectfully%20submitted%20that%20Article%20370%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20read%20or%20interpreted%20as%20an%20expression%20of%20power%20politics%20or%20a%20bargaining%20chip.%20Rather%2C%20it%20should%20be%20interpreted%20as%20a%20principled%20compact%20between%20the%20people%20of%20India%20(acting%20in%20their%20constituent%20capacity%20through%20the%20Indian%20Constituent%20Assembly)%20and%20the%20people%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20in%20constitutional%20arguments%2C%20there%20can%20be%20multiple%20approaches%20%E2%80%93%20One%20is%20a%20historical%20argument%2C%20second%20is%20a%20textual%20argument%2C%20third%20is%20a%20doctrinal%20argument%2C%20and%20the%20last%20is%20structural%20argument%20-%20these%20are%20all%20methods%20of%20constitutional%20interpretation%20and%20whichever%20way%20the%20court%20look%20at%20it%2C%20the%20end%20result%20will%20be%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20impugned%20orders%20-%20Constitution%20Orders-%20272%20(issued%20on%20August%205%2C%202019)%20and%20Constitution%20Order-%20273%20(issued%20on%20August%206%2C%202019)-%20in%20sum%20and%20substance%20do%20away%20with%20the%20Constitution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20That%20is%20impermissible%2C%20not%20authorised%20under%20the%20law%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Subramanium%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20counsel%20referred%20to%20Tuesday's%20observation%20of%20the%20CJI%20that%20in%20any%20representative%20democracy%2C%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20is%20expressed%20through%20established%20institutions%20under%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20going%20to%20urge%20that%20the%20expression%20Constituent%20Assembly%20and%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20a%20state%20are%20both%20institutions%20recognised%20under%20our%20Constitution%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20expressly%20affirmed%20by%20a%20resolution%20that%20they%20don't%20want%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20to%20be%20abrogated%20as%20they%20wanted%20the%20provision%20to%20be%20a%20language%20of%20communication%20between%20the%20two%20constitutions%20of%20India%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20is%20the%20body%20of%20people%2C%20has%20taken%20these%20proactive%20steps%20and%20we%20have%20accepted%20those%20proactive%20steps%2C%20can%20we%20unilaterally%20abrogate%20this%20arrangement%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned%2C%20while%20saying%20that%20this%20arrangement%20between%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20India%20was%20a%20compact%20of%20federalism%20and%20Article%20370%20establishes%20the%20contours%20of%20this%20relationship%20in%20the%20federal%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20told%20Subramanium%20by%20the%20Constitution%20order%20of%201954%2C%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20was%20adopted%20with%20certain%20omissions%20and%20modifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20one%20may%20call%20it%20a%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Constitution%20but%20in%20essence%20what%20was%20adopted%20was%20an%20Indian%20constitution%20with%20certain%20exceptions%20and%20modifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20its%20very%20nature%2C%20Article%20370%20is%20very%20flexible.%20Normally%20constitutions%20are%20flexible%20with%20time%20and%20space%20because%20they're%20made%20once%20but%20they%20last%20for%20a%20longer%20period%26quot%3B%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20told%20Mr%20Subramanium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20counsel%20said%20J%26amp%3BK%20constitution%20can%20be%20repealed%20only%20by%20state%20legislature%20and%20it%20cannot%20be%20abrogated%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Subramanium%20concluded%20his%20argument%20after%20which%20senior%20advocate%20Zafar%20Shah%20representing%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Bar%20Association%20commenced%20his%20submission%20and%20will%20continue%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20said%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20a%20Brexit-like%20referendum%20on%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20it%20said%2C%20is%20a%20constitutional%20democracy%20where%20the%20will%20of%20its%20people%20can%20be%20ascertained%20only%20through%20established%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrexit%20was%20the%20name%20given%20to%20the%20UK's%20departure%20from%20the%20European%20Union.%20Britain's%20exit%20from%20the%20EU%20was%20actuated%20by%20a%20rise%20in%20nationalistic%20fervour%2C%20daunting%20immigration%20issues%2C%20and%20a%20distressed%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20petitions%20challenging%20abrogation%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20which%20split%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories%20-%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Ladakh%20-%20were%20referred%20to%20a%2