%20FBI%20agents%20hours%20before%20the%20president%20was%20expected%20to%20land%20in%20the%20state%20Wednesday%2C%20authorities%20said.%3Cp%3E(Laura%20Seitz%2FThe%20Deseret%20News%20via%20AP)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFBI%20agents%20shot%20and%20killed%20an%20armed%20Utah%20man%20accused%20of%20threatening%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECraig%20Deleeuw%20Robertson%20was%20armed%20when%20agents%20arrived%20to%20serve%20a%20search%20warrant.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBiden%20was%20expected%20to%20to%20visit%20Utah%20around%20the%20time%20the%20threats%20were%20made%2C%20per%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20armed%20Utah%20man%20accused%20of%20making%20threats%20against%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fbiden-factory-jobs-new-mexico-manufacturing-renaissance-95700c62f45c3a69b03e550ebdcfa01b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20shot%20and%20killed%20by%20FBI%20agents%20hours%20before%20the%20president%20was%20expected%20to%20land%20in%20the%20state%20Wednesday%2C%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecial%20agents%20were%20trying%20to%20serve%20a%20warrant%20on%20the%20home%20of%20Craig%20Deleeuw%20Robertson%20in%20Provo%2C%20south%20of%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20when%20the%20shooting%20happened%20at%206%3A15%20a.m.%2C%20the%20FBI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobertson%20was%20armed%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20shooting%2C%20according%20to%20two%20law%20enforcement%20sources%20who%20spoke%20to%20The%20Associated%20Press%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20discuss%20details%20of%20an%20ongoing%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobertson%20posted%20online%20Monday%20that%20he%20had%20heard%20Biden%20was%20coming%20to%20Utah%20and%20he%20was%20planning%20to%20dig%20out%20a%20camouflage%20suit%20and%20%26quot%3Bclean%20the%20dust%20off%20the%20m24%20sniper%20rifle%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20scheduled%20to%20fly%20to%20Utah%20later%20in%20the%20day%20and%20visit%20a%20Veterans%20Affairs%20hospital%20in%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20Thursday%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20PACT%20Act%2C%20which%20expanded%20veterans%20benefits.%20He%20also%20planned%20to%20hold%20a%20reelection%20fundraiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobertson's%20posts%20indicated%20he%20did%20appear%20to%20own%20a%20long-range%20sniper%20rifle%20and%20numerous%20other%20weapons%2C%20as%20well%20as%20camouflage%20gear%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bghillie%20suit%2C%26quot%3B%20investigators%20said%20in%20court%20records.%20Robertson%20was%20charged%20under%20seal%20Tuesday%20with%20three%20felony%20counts%2C%20including%20making%20threats%20against%20the%20president%2C%20court%20documents%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20Robertson%20refers%20to%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BMAGA%20Trumper%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reference%20to%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%26quot%3B%20slogan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobertson%20also%20referenced%20a%20%26quot%3Bpresidential%20assassination%26quot%3B%20and%20made%20a%20long%20list%20of%20other%20online%20threats%2C%20including%20against%20top%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20overseeing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fdonald-trump-investigations-other-charges-b8b064a00caad4306fb54d2f6a320468%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourt%20cases%20against%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Manhattan%20District%20Attorney%20Alvin%20Bragg%2C%20U.S.%20Attorney%20General%20Merrick%20Garland%20and%20New%20York%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20time%20is%20right%20for%20a%20presidential%20assassination%20or%20two.%20First%20Joe%20then%20Kamala!!!%26quot%3B%20authorities%20say%20Robertson%20wrote%20in%20a%20September%202022%20Facebook%20post%20included%20in%20the%20filings.%20No%20attorney%20was%20immediately%20listed%20for%20Robertson%20in%20court%20documents%20and%20family%20members%20of%20Robertson%20could%20not%20be%20immediately%20reached%20for%20comment%20through%20publicly%20available%20phone%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20got%20a%20tip%20about%20the%20Bragg%20threat%20from%20Truth%20Social%20in%20March%2C%20after%20Robertson%20posted%20about%20%26quot%3Bwaiting%20in%20the%20courthouse%20parking%20garage%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20suppressed%20weapon%20and%20wanting%20to%20%26quot%3Bput%20a%20nice%20hole%20in%20his%20forehead.%26quot%3B%20His%20account%20has%20since%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20platform%20created%20by%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20further%20details%20were%20immediately%20released%20about%20the%20shooting%2C%20which%20is%20under%20review%20by%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Provo%20house%20where%20the%20confrontation%20apparently%20took%20place%20and%20which%20is%20connected%20with%20Robertson%20through%20public%20records%2C%20law%20enforcement%20could%20be%20seen%20Wednesday%20going%20in%20and%20out%20and%20removing%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20broken%20window%20could%20be%20seen%20next%20to%20the%20door%20and%20the%20blinds%20inside%20were%20askew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20leading%20to%20the%20house%20was%20blocked%20by%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20is%20just%20up%20the%20street%20from%20a%20meeting%20house%20of%20the%20Church%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20of%20Latter-day%20Saints%2C%20with%20the%20Wasatch%20Mountains%20rising%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravis%20Lee%20Clark%2C%20who's%20known%20Robertson%20for%20years%20from%20working%20at%20their%20church%20ward%20together%2C%20described%20Robertson%20as%20%26quot%3Bfrail%20of%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20masterful%20woodworker%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Bestablished%20icon%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20community.%20Robertson%20propped%20himself%20on%20a%20wood%20cane%20he'd%20carved%20himself%2C%20said%20Clark%2C%20who%20was%20surprised%