%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20plan%20to%20overturn%20the%20results%20of%20the%202020%20election%2C%20the%20NYT%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20was%20the%20first%20to%20report%20on%20and%20obtain%20the%20previously%20secret%20memo.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20campaign%20lawyers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fint.nyt.com%2Fdata%2Fdocumenttools%2Fchesebro-dec-6-memo%2Fce55d6abd79c2c71%2Ffull.pdf%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20previously%20secret%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20suggested%20telling%20people%20who%20were%20skeptical%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%20using%20fake%20electors%20that%20it%20was%20normal%20to%20have%20Trump's%20electors%20vote%20in%20losing%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F08%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-indictment-fake-electors-memo.html%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20obtained%20and%20reported%20on%20the%20memo%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20previously%20unknown%20campaign%20memo%20from%20December%202020%20%E2%80%94%20penned%20by%20then-Trump%20lawyer%20Kenneth%20Chesebro%20%E2%80%94%20outlined%20a%20plan%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Chesebro%20nor%20representatives%20for%20Trump%20immediately%20responded%20to%20Insider's%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20memo%2C%20the%20plan%20included%20having%20Trump-Pence%20electors%20in%20all%20six%20contested%20states%20send%20in%20certificates%20with%20their%20votes%20if%20one%20of%20the%20pending%20lawsuits%20looking%20into%20possible%20election%20interference%20was%20decided%20in%20the%20Trump%20campaign's%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChesebro%20wrote%20in%20the%20memo%20that%20their%20electors'%20votes%2C%20which%20would%20be%20cast%20in%20December%2C%20as%20well%20as%20news%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20would%20leak%20before%20the%20presidential%20certification%20on%20January%206.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20ends%20up%20deciding%20to%20have%20all%20of%20its%20electors%20vote%20on%20December%2014%2C%20even%20in%20States%20in%20which%20Trump%20has%20not%20been%20declared%20the%20winner%2C%20presumably%20word%20of%20this%20will%20leak%20out%20prior%20to%20December%2014%2C%26quot%3B%20Chesebro%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20should%20be%20messaging%20that%20presents%20this%20as%20a%20routine%20measure%20that%20is%20necessary.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Trump-Pence%20team%20should%20tell%20skeptics%20that%20they%20had%20their%20electors%20cast%20official%20votes%20in%20favor%20of%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20that%20in%20the%20event%20the%20courts%20(or%20state%20legislatures)%20were%20to%20later%20conclude%20that%20Trump%20actually%20won%20the%20state%2C%20the%20correct%20electoral%20slate%20can%20be%20counted%20in%20Congress%20in%20January%20just%20as%20the%20Democrats%20did%20in%20Hawaii%201960%2C%20which%20ended%20up%20with%20Hawaii's%20electoral%20votes%20being%20awarded%20to%20Kennedy%2C%20even%20though%20the%20litigation%20was%20not%20resolved%20until%20after%20the%20electors%20voted.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201960%2C%20Nixon%20won%20Hawaii%20by%20just%20140%20votes%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2022%2F02%2F07%2F1960-electoral-college-certificates-false-trump-electors-00006186%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitico%20reported%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20recount%20of%20the%20votes%20were%20underway%20when%20presidential%20electors%20met%20to%20cast%20their%20ballots.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Politico%20reported%2C%20Kennedy's%20elector%20nominees%20from%20the%20state%20signed%20certificates%20at%20the%20same%20time%20Nixon's%20electors%20did%2C%20even%20though%20Hawaii's%20governor%20had%20certified%20Nixon's%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20existence%20of%20this%20campaign%20memo%20was%20revealed%20in%20Trump's%20indictment%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20January%206%20riot%20last%20week%2C%20but%20details%20of%20it%20were%20not%20known%20until%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20on%20it%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20reported%20that%20prosecutors%20in%20the%20January%206%20case%20against%20Trump%20are%20now%20using%20the%20memo%20as%20a%20link%20to%20underline%20their%20allegations%20that%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20committed%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20overturn%20the%20election%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lawyer-suggested-scheme-overturning-election-memo-nyt-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691613736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6488af32d4e551001974e02e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lawyer-suggested-scheme-overturning-election-memo-nyt-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20idea%20was%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20plan%20to%20overturn%20the%20results%20of%20the%202020%20election%2C%20according%20to%20a%20memo%20obtained%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rcohen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Cohen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lawyer-suggested-scheme-overturning-election-memo-nyt-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%206%20killed%20in%20wildfires%20that%20devastated%20parts%20of%20the%20Hawaiian%20island%20of%20Maui%2C%20official%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691613579000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102584279%2Cimgsize-1129944.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fwor