%3B%20on%20the%20app%20in%20rapid%20succession%20%E2%80%94%20could%20cause%20even%20more%20chaos%20and%20disruption%20than%20they%20already%20do%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20a%20Starbucks%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Starbucks%20drive-thru%20lanes%20often%20see%20lines%20of%20cars%20wrapping%20around%20the%20building%20or%20into%20the%20street%2C%20Target%20has%20taken%20a%20step%20that%20should%20prevent%20order%20volumes%20from%20getting%20too%20far%20out%20of%20hand%3A%20Customers%20will%20need%20to%20buy%20something%20for%20pick-up%20from%20Target's%20app%20or%20website%20in%20order%20to%20access%20the%20Starbucks%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20could%20also%20help%20boost%20sales%20numbers%20for%20the%20retailer%2C%20which%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeauty-shoppers-still-spending-big-as-us-consumers-cut-elsewhere-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiencing%20a%20slump%20in%20recent%20quarters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221185%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshots%20of%20Starbucks%20ordering%20in%20the%20Target%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3dae4a8ce53001a59371a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22922%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Target%20app%20will%20prompt%20drive-up%20customers%20to%20add%20a%20Starbucks%20item%20to%20their%20order%20and%20to%20customize%20it.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.target.com%2Fpress%2FFact-Sheets%2F2022%2F11%2FAbout-Starbucks-with-Target-Drive-Up-Our-New-Fulfi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20it%20works%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20the%20shopper%20places%20an%20order%20for%20drive-up%2C%20which%20Target%20says%20will%20be%20ready%20in%20two%20hours%20or%20less.%20There%20is%20no%20minimum%20order