ers%2C%20Modi%20has%20given%20the%20slogans%20%E2%80%99Corruption%20Quit%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Dynasty%20Quit%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Appeasement%20Quit%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20said%20that%20while%20the%20opposition%20may%20lack%20confidence%20in%20the%20government%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20have%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20confidence%E2%80%9D%20in%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Manipur%20is%20not%20divided%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20shot%20back%20at%20Gandhi%20for%20his%20speech%2C%20where%20he%20alleged%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Cmurdered%E2%80%9D%20Bharat%20%3Cem%3EMata%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20history%2C%20someone%20has%20talked%20about%20the%20murder%20of%20Bharat%20Mata%2C%20while%20leaders%20from%20the%20Congress%20clapped%20and%20thumped%20their%20desks%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Irani%20who%20spoke%20right%20after%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%20is%20not%20divided%2C%20it%20is%20a%20part%20of%20this%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20member%20of%20his%20alliance%20said%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20that%20India%20only%20means%20north%20India.%20If%20he%20has%20the%20courage%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20comment%20and%20ask%20for%20an%20explanation.%20Another%20Congress%20leader%20said%20there%20should%20be%20a%20referendum%20on%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%A6%20Was%20the%20statement%20given%20as%20per%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Congress%20leadership%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrani%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20exodus%20of%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20in%201990s%20and%20the%20anti-Sikh%20riots%20in%201984%2C%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20not%20acting%20on%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20not%20India%20because%20you%20define%20corruption%20in%20India%2C%20you%20define%20incompetence%20%E2%80%A6%20you%20are%20not%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Speech%3A%20An%20Alliance%20Leader%20Steering%20the%20Ideological%20Beliefs%20of%20INDIA%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-speech-ideology-india-alliance%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Speech%3A%20An%20Alliance%20Leader%20Steering%20the%20Ideological%20Beliefs%20of%20INDIA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFailure%20of%20%E2%80%98double%20engine%E2%80%99%20government%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20centred%20their%20attack%20on%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20engine%E2%80%9D%20government%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanata%20Dal%20(United)%20MP%20Rajiv%20Ranjan%20Singh%20said%20that%20even%20though%20Manipur%20has%20a%20double%20engine%20government%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20brings%20up%20instances%20from%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%20has%20a%20double%20engine%20government%20of%20the%20BJP.%20When%20we%20discuss%20Manipur%2C%20the%20government%20brings%20instances%20from%20other%20states.%20Today%20it%20is%20Manipur%2C%20tomorrow%20it%20will%20be%20Mizoram%20%E2%80%93%20your%20entire%20northeastern%20borders%20will%20be%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLong%20speeches%20were%20given%20%5Bby%20BJP%20MPs%5D%20but%20Manipur%20was%20not%20mentioned.%20There%20is%20trust%20deficit%20between%20two%20communities%20in%20Manipur%20and%20towards%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20MPs%20listing%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20have%20proved%20that%20they%20are%20not%20bothered%20about%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20%5BSmriti%20Irani%5D%20and%20all%20other%20speakers%20have%20proved%20that%20they%20are%20not%20bothered%20about%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20and%20are%20only%20interested%20in%20beating%20the%20drums%20about%20their%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20double%20engine%2C%20you%20just%20need%20one%20engine%20and%20one%20driver%20like%20we%20have%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20civil%20war%20%5Bin%20Manipur%5D%20and%20a%20government%20that%20cannot%20control%20a%20civil%20war%20has%20no%20business%20to%20remain%20in%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43-1024x775.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43-1024x775.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43-300x227.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%201170w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-651628%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22636%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20near-complete%20separation%20between%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20and%20minority%20tribal%20Kuki%20communities.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40MangteC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20MP%20Kanimozhi%20said%20that%20the%20double%20engine%20government%20in%20Manipur%20is%20what%20has%20led%20to%20its%20current%20state%20of%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20says%20there%20is%20a%20double%20engine%20in%20Manipur.%20But%20this%20double%20engine%20has%20become%20a%20double-edged%20weapon%2C%20double%20disaster%20for%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20PM%20speaks%20outside%20parliament%20but%20refuses%20to%20cross%20the%20threshold%20and%20come%20inside%20the%20parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20MP%20Nama%20Nageswara%20Rao%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20should%20take%20an%20all-party%20delegation%20to%20Manipur%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20responsibility%20for%20what%20is%20happening%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Win%20people%E2%80%99s%20hearts%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20also%20saw%20two%20Union%20ministers%20warring%20with%20National%20Conference%20MP%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20over%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20said%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20should%20act%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20whole%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20PM%20does%20not%20represent%20only%20one%20colour.%20He%20represents%20the%201.4%20billion%20people%20of%20India.%20I%20tried%20to%20bring%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20back%20home%20when%20Gujral%20was%20PM%20and%20forces%20across%20the%20border%20killed%20innocent%20Kashmiri%20Pandits.%20We%20stopped%20the%2050%20vehicles%20to%20bring%20them%20back%20home.%20How%20many%20Pandits%20have%20you%20brought%20back%20in%20ten%20years%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%20Nityanand%20Rai%20stood%20up%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cwrong%E2%80%9D%20to%20say%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20done%20anything%20for%20Kashmiri%20Pandits.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20misleading%E2%80%9D%2C%20Rai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20also%20said%20that%20whether%20it%20is%20Kashmir%20or%20Manipur%2C%20the%20message%20of%20love%20should%20be%20sent%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20work%20with%20love%20and%20win%20people%E2%80%99s%20hearts.%20Love%20is%20the%20only%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20MP%20Harsimrat%20Kaur%20Badal%20also%20said%20that%20the%20politics%20of%20hate%20will%20not%20solve%20anything%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20doing%20politics%20of%20hate%2C%20the%20government%20should%20provide%20its%20healing%20touch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20from%20the%20YSRCP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20however%2C%20received%20support%20from%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20(YSCRP)%2C%20which%20said%20that%20while%20the%20party%20will%20support%20the%20government%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20Manipur%20needs%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.V.%20Mithun%20Reddy%2C%20YSRCP%20MP%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cheinous%20crimes%20against%20women%E2%80%9D%20are%20being%20seen%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEthnic%20violence%20needs%20to%20be%20curbed.%20Both%20the%20ethnic%20groups%20need%20to%20be%20made%20to%20sit%20for%20a%20dialogue.%20This%20is%20really%20shameful%20that%20this%20is%20happening%20in%20our%20country%20where%20we%20preach%20unity%20in%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAddress%20the%20source%20of%20the%20problem%20through%20meaningful%20dialogue.%20A%20strong%20Manipur%20means%20a%20strong%20India.%20YSRCP%20believes%20that%20this%20no-confidence%20motion%20does%20not%20carry%20much%20value%2C%20because%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20has%20an%20absolute%20majority.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20tussle%20between%20two%20alliances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20urge%20the%20government%20to%20sort%20out%20Manipur%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20government%20should%20act%20with%20all%20its%20might%20