ocracy%E2%80%99%20if%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Is%20Implemented%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F04101723%2FScreenshot-2022-05-04-at-10.17.19-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20race%20to%20win%20over%20the%20public%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20election%20in%20India%20has%20begun%20in%20full%20force.%20The%20unification%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%20is%20a%20significant%20indicator%20of%20their%20efforts.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20potential%20%E2%80%98magic%20bullet%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20remain%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20is%20known%20about%20the%20draft%20UCC%2C%20but%20the%20%E2%80%98hot%20potato%E2%80%99%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20policy%20and%20judicial%20system%E2%80%99s%20concoction%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20desire%20to%20centrally%20legislate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20UCC%20is%20one%20of%20many%20directive%20principles%20listed%20in%20Article%2044%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20it%20does%20not%20impose%20a%20time%20frame%20nor%20does%20it%20provide%20for%20the%20overruling%20of%20Articles%2025-28%20that%20guarantee%20religious%20freedom%20to%20all%20citizens%20and%20allows%20them%20to%20maintain%20their%20own%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirective%20Principles%20do%20not%20carry%20the%20same%20legal%20weight%20as%20Fundamental%20Rights%2C%20which%20are%20the%20subject%20of%20Articles%2025-28.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20UCC%20must%20be%20codified%2C%20it%20can%20only%20be%20done%20after%20extensive%20consultations%20with%20the%20so-called%20religious%20leaders%2C%20experts%2C%20and%20the%20common%20citizenry%20across%20regions%20and%20religions%20of%20India.%20It%20cannot%20be%20a%20referendum%2C%20as%20a%20plural%20democracy%20is%20only%20as%20good%20as%20its%20many%20minorities%20feel%20it%20is!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2044%20encourages%20the%20State%20to%20secure%20a%20UCC%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20by%20eliminating%20discrepancies%20between%20various%20personal%20laws%20in%20use%20currently%20and%20treated%20equally%20through%20codifying%20civil%20issues.%20Various%20aspects%20of%20personal%20lives%20such%20as%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20maintenance%2C%20inheritance%2C%20adoption%2C%20and%20succession%20of%20the%20property%20are%20the%20focus%20of%20such%20a%20code.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20the%20premise%20that%20there%20is%20no%20connection%20between%20religion%20and%20law%20in%20modern%20civilisation%3B%20matters%20identified%20as%20%3Cem%3Enon-justiciable%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20not%20to%20be%20challenged%20in%20the%20court%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Muslim%20law%20in%20India%20is%20not%20codified%2C%20and%20hearing%20whatever%20ruling%20party%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20prime%20minister%20have%20said%2C%20the%20UCC%20proposition%20is%20likely%20to%20directly%20impact%20the%20Muslims%20and%20multitude%20of%20tribal%20communities%20across%20India%2C%20socially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20India%20has%20a%20Muslim%20population%20of%20around%20200%20million%2C%20with%20approximately%20half%2C%20about%20100%20million%2C%20engaged%20in%20the%20labour%20force.%20A%20majority%20of%20these%20workers%20work%20under%20contracts%20set%20by%20a%20non-Muslim.%20Therefore%2C%20any%20policy%20change%20impacting%20the%20Muslim%20labour%20force%20will%20also%20affect%20the%20non-Muslim%20population%2C%20economically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20focus%20on%20the%20Muslim%20law%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20extremely%20complex%20diversity%20in%20religious%20ritual%20practices%20and%20innumerable%20sources%20of%20%E2%80%98community%20specific%20common%20practices%E2%80%99%2C%20arriving%20at%20one%20unified%20law%20for%20civil%20matters%20is%20difficult%2C%20if%20not%20impossible.%20There%20are%20several%20grey%20%3Cem%3Eareas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20making%20a%20judgment%20and%20authenticating%20a%20practice%20may%20not%20meet%20modern%20and%20global%20standards%20of%20civility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20essential%20parameters%20that%20define%20gender%20empowerment%20such%20as%20deciding%20the%20marriageable%20age%2C%20(widow)%20remarriage%2C%20practice%20of%20bride%20price%20or%20dowry%2C%20polygamy.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20other%20aspects%20which%20are%20also%20important%20to%20consider%20such%20as%20food%20habits%2C%20burial%20practices%2C%20rules%20of%20household%2C%20and%20family%20formation%20(matriarchal)%2C%20and%20cohabitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20ensure%20gender%20equality%20in%20%3Cem%3Esuccession%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20wealth%20and%20property%2C%20how%20can%20one%20enforce%20%3Cem%3Emaintenance%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20modern%20world%20where%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20a%20woman%20is%20an%20earning%20member%2C%20while%20men%20are%20out%20of%20employment%20and%20even%20the%20labour%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concepts%20and%20practices%20of%20%3Cem%3EZakat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(charitable%20distribution%20of%20a%20share%20of%20total%20annual%20wealth)%20and%20%3Cem%3EWakaf%20%3C%2Fem%3E(eternal%20bequeath%20of%20riches%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20human%20welfare)%20are%20the%20foundations%20of%20Islamic%20jurisprudence.%20Emulating%20these%20concepts%20formally%20can%20bring%20about%20a%20transformative%20infusion%20of%20finance%20to%20the%20Indian%20society%E2%80%99s%20economic%20system%20that%20could%20ensure%20poverty%20alleviation%20and%20increase%20community%20level%20economic%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Ffavour-of-uniform-civil-code-want-total-gender-equality-javed-akhtar%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20in%20Favour%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20but%20What%20I%20Want%20Is%20Total%20Gender%20Equality%E2%80%99%3A%20Javed%20Akhtar%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20politics%2C%20policy%20framework%2C%20and%20its%20implications%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UCC%20poses%20a%20potential%20threat%20to%20specific%20communities%20and%20the%20entire%20citizenry%20of%20India.%20It%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20precursor%20to%20the%20policy%20designs%20that%20would%20follow%20if%20the%20current%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20wins%20the%20general%20election%20for%20a%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20using%20the%20UCC%20%E2%80%93%20which%20surrounds%20a%20hype%20of%20teaching%20the%20Muslims%20a%20lesson%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ruling%20party%20aims%20to%20consolidate%20the%20Hindu%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20response%20to%20such%20overtures%20should%20be%20to%20legally%20challenge%20the%20contradictions%20and%20demand%20that%20the%20draft%20of%20the%20UCC%20must%20first%20be%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20for%20discussion%20and%20then%20enable%20the%20larger%20community%20organisations%20to%20comment%20on%20it.%20It%20is%20futile%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20judicial%20system%20to%20seek%20opinions%20on%20the%20UCC%20as%20a%20written%20draft%20is%20unavailable%20for%20the%20people%20to%20read%2C%20understand%2C%20and%20comment%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98stealth%E2%80%99%20passage%20of%20a%20law%20could%20create%20huge%20social%20furor%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20the%20new%20government%20will%20be%20empowered%20to%20design%20rules%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202019%20(CAA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAA%E2%80%99s%20implementation%20is%20anchored%20upon%20the%20preparation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98national%20register%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20further%20entirely%20depends%20on%20the%20preparation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98national%20population%20register%E2%80%99%20(NPR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F08175010%2Ffile78fz3cmg4nm1cil63gn2-1231436800-1576740089.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F08175010%2Ffile78fz3cmg4nm1cil63gn2-1231436800-1576740089.jpg%20700w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F08175010%2Ffile78fz3cmg4nm1cil63gn2-1231436800-1576740089-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-606459%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22609%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStudents%20hold%20placards%20as%20they%20raise%20slogans%20during%20a%20protest%20against%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20at%20Maulana%20Azad%20National%20Urdu%20University%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20December%2017%2C%202019.%20Photo%3A%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20current%20design%2C%20the%20NPR%20will%20be%20prepared%20through%20and%20during%20the%20next%20round%20of%20the%20Indian%20Census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20as%20to%20why%20the%20decadal%20census%20has%20been%20delayed%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%20since%202021%20and%20despite%20the%20nation%20being%20declared%20COVID-free.%20And%20this%20has%20happened%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20150%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInnumerable%20critical%20errors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20potential%20communal%20unrest%20looms%20if%20the%20NPR%20questions%20are%20canvassed%20during%20the%20next%20round%20of%20the%20Indian%20Census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inclusion%20of%20the%20NPR%20data%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Census%2C%20during%20the%20same%20visits%20is%20a%20critical%20error%20of%20administrative%20judgment%20and%20perceived%20as%20a%20political%20conspiracy%20against%20the%20Muslims%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20objective%20of%20the%20Census%20is%20to%20create%20a%20reliable%20source%20of%20general%20demographic%20information%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20formulating%20government%20policies%20and%20academic%20research.%20It%20is%20%3Cem%3Enot%20%3C%2Fem%3Eintended%20to%20provide%20individualised%20information%20to%20be%20used%20against%20respondents%20in%20subsequent%20proceedings%20that%20seriously%20jeopardise%20the%20individual%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20liberty%2C%20and%20dignity%2C%20such%20as%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20registry%2C%20omission%20from%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20statelessness%2C%20prolonged%20detention%20and%20deportation%20for%20a%20person%20who%20obeyed%20Indian%20law%20by%20responding%20to%20a%20census%20enumerator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Indian%20law%2C%20the%20collection%20of%20data%20by%20the%20Census%20of%20India%20Act%2C%201948%20cannot%20be%20used%20otherwise%20and%20cannot%20be%20presented%20for%20legal%20judgments.%20Thus%2C%20the%20NPR%2C%20if%20tagged%20along%20with%20the%20Census%2C%20could%20be%20termed%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20administrative%20activity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20Section%2015%20of%20the%20Census%20Act%20says%20that%20the%20Census%20data%20should%20not%20be%20used%20against%20a%20census%20respondent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20provides%2C%20first%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20person%E2%80%9D%20has%20the%20right%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinspect%20any%20book%2C%20register%20or%20record%20made%20by%20a%20census%20officer%20in%20the%20discharge%20of%20his%20duty%20taking%20the%20census%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20confidentiality%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20census%20information%20cannot%20be%20protected%20if%20the%20information%20is%20to%20be%20transmitted%20directly%20into%20the%20NRC%20and%20then%20used%20against%20the%20individual%20in%20a%20Foreigners%20Tribunal%20proceeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritically%2C%20Section%2015%20of%20the%20Census%20Act%20also%20provides%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20entry%20in%20any%20such%20book%2C%20register%2C%20record%20or%20schedule%20shall%20be%20admissible%20as%20evidence%20%3Cem%3Ein%20any%20civil%20proceeding%20whatsoever%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20added).%20This%20provision%20would%20necessarily%20have%20to%20be%20violated%20if%20purported%20evidence%20as%20to%20the%20citizenship%20of%20an%20individual%20were%20to%20be%20admitted%20in%20evidence%20in%20a%20Foreigners%20Tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20the%20Census%20Act%20nowhere%20mentions%20the%20NRC%20since%20the%20Census%20Act%20was%20enacted%20in%201948%2C%20but%20the%20NRC%2C%20as%20it%20is%20currently%20contemplated%2C%20only%20came%20into%20conceptual%20existence%20through%20Citizenship%20Rules%20formulated%20in%202003.%20Significantly%2C%20while%20the%20Census%20Act%20has%20been%20amended%20on%20more%20than%20one%20occasion%2C%20it%20has%20never%20been%20amended%20to%20authorise%20the%20practice%20of%20using%20census%20officers%2C%20duly%20authorised%20under%20the%20Census%20Act%2C%20to%20collect%20data%20that%20will%20be%20used%20to%20create%20the%20NRC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20fallout%20of%20the%20NPR-linked%20NRC%20will%20be%20the%20exclusion%20of%20millions%20of%20genuine%20citizens%20from%20the%20electoral%20rolls.%20Yet%20the%20wildcard%20use%20of%20CAA%20can%20authorise%20even%20executed%20Hindus%20to%20vote%3B%20while%20only%20the%20Muslims%20who%20will%20be%20made%20ineligible%20to%20vote%20pending%20the%20Foreigners%20Tribunal%20authorisation.%20Even%20if%20the%20government%20carries%20out%20the%20joint%20exercise%20of%20NPR%20and%20NRC%20after%20proper%20legal%20amendments%2C%20it%20will%20still%20end%20up%20hurting%20the%20Muslims%20since%20all%20other%20religious%20communities%20will%20be%20rescued%20by%20the%202019%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%2C%20therefore%2C%20argues%20that%20as%20a%20first%20step%20in%20resolving%20the%20onset%20of%20serious%20social%20and%20economic%20disturbances%2C%20the%20Indian%20census%20operations%20must%20be%20delinked%20from%20the%20proposed%20collection%20of%20data%20for%20the%20preparation%20of%20NPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhat-the-proposed-uniform-civil-code-should-not-be%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%20Proposed%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Should%20%E2%80%93%20And%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%93%20Be%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20ground%20issues%20need%20to%20be%20solved%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20major%20economic%20issues%20that%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at%20if%20the%20UCC%20is%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20multi-layer%20bureaucracy%20and%20administration%20such%20as%20the%20IAS%2C%20IPS%20and%20state-level%20services%20is%20the%20one%20sustaining%20the%20democracy%20and%20development%20projects%20of%20India%2C%20it%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20that%20Muslims%2C%20like%20all%20other%20identity%20groups%2C%20assert%20their%20rights%20as%20Indian%20citizens%20and%20ensure%20a%20close%20participation%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20institutions%20such%20as%20the%20panchayats.%20They%20should%20get%20connected%20and%20associated%20with%20the%20local%20(village%20and%20urban%20ward)%20level%20institutions%20and%20bureaucracy%20such%20as%20the%20ICDS%2C%20the%20panchayat%2C%20primary%20school%2C%20village%20accountant%2C%20small%20scale%20industries%2C%20public%20and%20private%20markets%2C%20local%20bank%20and%20police%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20that%20the%20Muslim%20community%20finds%20easier%20access%20to%20mainstream%20schooling%20and%20the%20college%20system%20to%20be%20able%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98exclusionary%E2%80%99%20and%20poor-quality%20education%20system%2C%20managed%20by%20minority%20communities%2C%20which%20is%20so%20willingly%20promoted%20by%20the%20state%20and%20national%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20only%204%25%20of%20Muslim%20children%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Flike-everyone-else-muslims-too-want-a-proper-education%5C%22%3Ego%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20madrasa%20and%20maktab%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Sachar%20Committee%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELabour%20market%20interdependence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20population%20amounts%20to%20approximately%20200%20million%2C%20with%20roughly%20half%2C%20that%20is%20100%20million%2C%20actively%20participating%20in%20the%20labour%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20Muslim%20workers%20in%20India%20are%20either%20self-employed%2C%20engaged%20in%20managing%20their%20own%20businesses%2C%20or%20employed%20in%20manufacturing%20and%20manual%20labour.%20Each%20of%20these%20workers%20has%20employment%20contracts%20with%20at%20least%20one%20non-Muslim%20Indian%2C%20primarily%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F14124415%2F2020_5img13_May_2020_PTI13-05-2020_000137B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F14124415%2F2020_5img13_May_2020_PTI13-05-2020_000137B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F14124415%2F2020_5img13_May_2020_PTI13-05-2020_000137B-300x160.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F14124415%2F2020_5img13_May_2020_PTI13-05-2020_000137B-1024x545.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-454463%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22639%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Workers%20at%20an%20apparel%20manufacturing%20company%20in%20Noida%20during%20the%20COVID-19-induced%20lockdown.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20any%20social%2C%20bureaucratic%2C%20or%20politically%20motivated%20policies%20that%20impact%20the%20Muslim%20labour%20force%20will%20also%20affect%20their%20non-Muslim%20counterparts%2C%20effectively%20doubling%20the%20impact%20on%20around%20200%20million%20workers%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20converts%20to%20about%2032%25%20of%20the%20overall%20labour%20force%2C%20directly%20affecting%20the%20GDP%20to%20the%20same%20proportion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20transformative%20reduction%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%20about%2010%25%20decline%20in%20labour%20productivity%2C%20will%20amount%20to%20a%20huge%20decline%20of%20about%201%25%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20GDP%2C%20which%20would%20further%20impede%20future%20growth%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5BNote%20that%20all%20estimates%20mentioned%20in%20this%20article%20are%20based%20on%200nly%2010%25%20decline%20in%20labour%20productivity.%20If%20this%20percentage%20increases%2C%20the%20total%20impact%20will%20be%20much%20more%20than%201%25%20of%20the%20GDP.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20sociology%20of%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20First%E2%80%99%20growth%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20structure%20of%20modern%20labour%20supply%20in%20India%20is%20uniquely%20lopsided%20favouring%20the%20high%20castes%20who%20are%20socially%20and%20economically%20better-off.%20The%20so-called%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20Hindus%20are%20disproportionately%20represented%20in%20the%20organised%20sector%20jobs%2C%20both%20in%20the%20government%20and%20private%20sectors%2C%20and%20in%20higher-level%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20has%20excluded%20large%20proportions%20of%20the%20people%20belonging%20to