tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fcaa-protests-will-seize-properties-of-those-who-indulge-in-violence-says-yogi-adityanath-1629778-2019-12-19%5C%22%3E%20directed%3C%2Fa%3E%20authorities%20to%20seize%20properties%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20protests%20against%20the%20CAA%3B%20it%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcurrent-affairs%2Fup-govt-drops-notices-to-seize-properties-of-anti-caa-protesters-122021800113_1.html%5C%22%3Ewithdrew%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blatant%20majoritarianism%20and%20the%20impositions%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CHindu-first%E2%80%9D%20ideology%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20pluralist%20ethos%20of%20India%2C%20will%20have%20an%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20and%20liberties%20of%20ordinary%20Indians%20and%20their%20capacity%20to%20contribute%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20is%20a%20land%20of%20a%20million%20markets%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20economy%20is%20unique%20and%20highly%20complex.%20It%20is%20a%20mixed%20economy%2C%20as%20it%20showcases%20elements%20of%20both%20modernisation%20and%20traditionalism%20in%20the%20production%20and%20consumption%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2080%25%20of%20the%20economy%20is%20unorganised%20with%20self-employed%20and%20unregulated%20production%20sectors.%20In%202018-19%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcprindia.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2FInformality_Explainer_Dec2020.pdf%5C%22%3Eonly%2019%25%20of%20the%20total%20labour%20force%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20written%20employment%20and%20work%20contract%2C%20and%20who%20could%20be%20classified%20as%20regular%20salaried%20employees.%20This%20calls%20for%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20new%20and%20innovative%20institutions%20to%20establish%20new%20markets%2C%20which%20are%20technology%20driven%2C%20thereby%20improving%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20markets%20such%20as%20the%20local%20farmers%E2%80%99%20markets%2C%20providing%20a%20variety%20of%20products%2C%20rural%20markets%20(retail%20and%20wholesale)%2C%20sub-urban%20thrift%20markets%2C%20urban%20markets%2C%20and%20online%20markets%20offer%20innumerable%20opportunities%20to%20consumers%2C%20producers%2C%20and%20suppliers.%20Nowhere%20in%20the%20world%20one%20can%20get%20essential%20medicine%20or%20even%20coffee%20packed%20in%20a%20small%20package%20sold%20for%20as%20little%20as%20Rs%202%2C%20or%202.8%20US%20cents%2C%20as%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20get%20a%20fully%20satisfying%20meal%20for%20as%20little%20as%20Rs%2050%2C%20or%20about%2055%20US%20cents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20India%20possesses%20huge%20markets%2C%20for%20example%2C%20over%20800%20million%20subscribers%20are%20registered%20cell%20phone%20users%20with%20an%20average%20monthly%20user%20bill%20of%20Rs%20275%20or%20just%20about%20%244.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20may%20have%20its%20merits%2C%20it%20must%20be%20approached%20with%20sensitivity%2C%20respecting%20the%20religious%20freedom%20and%20cultural%20diversity%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20upcoming%202024%20General%20Election%20and%20the%20potential%20implications%20of%20policies%20like%20the%20NPR%2C%20as%20discussed%20earlier%2C%20demand%20vigilance%20from%20all%20citizens%20to%20safeguard%20the%20principles%20of%20democracy%20and%20social%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20continues%20on%20its%20path%20of%20growth%20and%20development%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20embrace%20pluralism%20and%20foster%20an%20environment%20of%20mutual%20respect%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20cooperation%20among%20different%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20promoting%20divisive%20ideologies%2C%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20creating%20institutions%20and%20policies%20that%20uplift%20all%20sections%20of%20society.%20This%20would%20ensure%20inclusive%20economic%20growth%2C%20and%20equal%20opportunities%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fabusaleh-shariff%5C%22%3EAbusaleh%20Shariff%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ashariff%40usindiapolicy.org)%20is%20chief%20scholar%20at%20the%20US-India%20Policy%20Institute.%20He%20was%20Member%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20High%20Level%20(Sachar%20Committee)%20during%202005-07.%20He%20was%20also%20Chief%20Economist%20at%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Applied%20Economic%20Research%20for%20about%2020%20years.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EViews%20expressed%20are%20his%20own%20and%20do%20not%20represent%20any%20institution%20or%20organisation%20he%20belongs%20to.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691577033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F04101723%2FScreenshot-2022-05-04-at-10.17.19-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-social-and-economic-dangers-to-the-mother-of-democracy-if-a-uniform-civil-code-is-implemented%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20may%20have%20its%20merits%2C%20it%20must%20be%20approached%20with%20sensitivity%2C%20respecting%20the%20religious%20freedom%20and%20cultural%20diversity%20of%20the%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-social-and-economic-dangers-to-the-mother-of-democracy-if-a-uniform-civil-code-is-implemented%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98BeerBiceps%E2%80%99%20Interview%20of%20J.%20Sai%20Deepak%20Violates%20Community%20Standards%2C%20But%20YouTube%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Take%20It%20Down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09113747%2Fjsd-bb.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98BeerBiceps%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20with%20more%20than%2058%20lakh%20subscribers.%20The%20founder%20of%20this%20channel%20is%20Ranveer%20Allahabadia%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20headlines%20recently%20for%20his%20video%20interviews%20with%20several%20ministers%20and%20politicians%2C%20including%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20Smriti%20Irani.%20The%20description%20of%20these%20YoutUbe%20videos%20says%20%E2%80%9CCollaboration%20with%20MyGovIndia%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F06%2F27%2Fno-payment-no-tender-just-an-opportunity-untangling-the-beerbiceps-collab-with-modi-ministers%5C%22%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20Allahabadia%20and%20his%20partner%20Viraj%20Seth%20stated%20a%20representative%20from%20the%20government%20approached%20them%20in%20May%20and%20suggested%20inviting%20some%20key%20cabinet%20ministers%20on%20their%20podcast.%20He%20revealed%20that%20he%20agreed%20to%20the%20idea%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20discussion.%20The%20idea%20for%20this%20programme%20came%20from%20MyGov%20(a%20citizen%20engagement%20platform%20launched%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%202014%20to%20promote%20the%20participation%20of%20citizens%20in%20governance)%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9CCollaboration%20with%20MyGovIndia%E2%80%9D%20was%20used%20for%20these%20interviews.%20He%20also%20clarified%20that%20he%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20payment%20from%20the%20government%20for%20these%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98BeerBiceps%E2%80%99%20YouTube%20channel%20Ranveer%20Allahabadia%20has%20collaborated%20with%20a%20number%20of%20right-wing%20influencers.%20Among%20them%20are%20Rajeev%20Malhotra%2C%20Vikram%20Sampath%2C%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal%2C%20J.%20Sai%20Deepak%2C%20Abhijit%20Iyer%2C%20and%20Anand%20Ranganathan.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F06%2F27%2Fno-payment-no-tender-just-an-opportunity-untangling-the-beerbiceps-collab-with-modi-ministers%5C%22%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20creator%20added%20that%20he%20was%20planning%20to%20invite%20guests%20from%20the%20Left%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20video%20of%20Allahbadia%20is%20gathering%20widespread%20traction%20on%20social%20media.%20In%20it%2C%20he%20asks%20his%20podcast%20guest%2C%20the%20right-leaning%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20J.%20Sai%20Deepak%2C%20to%20name%20three%20people%20who%20should%20leave%20India%20and%20never%20come%20back.%20The%20question%20itself%20is%20problematic%2C%20and%20the%20answer%20is%20fueled%20by%20hate%2C%20in%20which%20Deepak%20names%20two%20prominent%20intellectuals%20of%20India%20and%20a%20senior%20journalist.%20Following%20the%20release%20of%20the%20episode%2C%20all%20three%20have%20been%20facing%20harassment%20and%20cyberbullying%20on%20social%20media.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20a%20May%205%20episode%20titled%20%E2%80%9CAdvocate%20J%20Sai%20Deepak%20Opens%20Up%20On%20CAA%2C%20Modi%2C%20%26amp%3B%20India%E2%80%99s%20Democracy%20%7C%20AJIO%20Presents%20TRS%E2%80%9D%20is%20rife%20with%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20false%20claims%2C%20hate%20speech%20and%20religious%20intolerance%20towards%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20the%20offensive%20nature%20of%20the%20video%2C%20we%20sent%20YouTube%20a%20detailed%20note%20regarding%20this%20video%E2%80%99s%20violation%20of%20their%20policies.%20A%20YouTube%20spokesperson%20replied%20that%20following%20a%20thorough%20review%20of%20the%20video%20against%20the%20platform%E2%80%99s%20Community%20Guidelines%2C%20they%20had%20come%20to%20the%20decision%20that%20it%20did%20not%20violate%20any%20of%20YouTube%E2%80%99s%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20article%2C%20we%20will%20review%20clips%20from%20the%20video%20with%20timestamps%20and%20demonstrate%20how%20it%20violates%20YouTube%E2%80%99s%20own%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHarassment%20and%20Cyberbullying%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20the%2056%3A30%20mark%2C%20host%20Allahbadia%20asks%20the%20advocate%20to%20name%20three%20people%20who%20should%20leave%20India%20and%20never%20come%20back.%20He%20replies%20with%20the%20names%20of%20three%20prominent%20Indian%20intellectuals%20including%20Romila%20Thapar%2C%20Professor%20Irfan%20Habib%20and%20Barkha%20Dutt.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20Romila%20Thapar%20and%20Irfan%20Habib%20are%20historians%20of%20international%20repute%20and%20Barkha%20Dutt%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%20All%20of%20them%20are%20often%20targeted%20as%20active%20players%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98conspiracy%E2%80%99%20to%20break%20up%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20here%20that%20as%20per%20the%20YouTube%20Community%20Guidelines%2C%20both%20the%20question%20and%20answer%20are%20condemnable.%20The%20host%20of%20this%20podcast%20asks%20a%20question%2C%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20answer%20it%2C%20as%20the%20guest%20did%2C%20was%20by%20naming%20prominent%20individuals%20and%20promoting%20hate%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20YouTube%E2%80%99s%20policy%20on%20Harassment%20and%20Cyberbullying.%20YouTube%E2%80%99s%20policy%20on%20this%20is%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EContent%20that%20targets%20an%20individual%20or%20group%20with%20prolonged%20or%20malicious%20slurs%20based%20on%20their%20protected%20group%20status%20or%20intrinsic%20characteristics%2C%20including%20physical%20characteristics%2C%20is%20not%20allowed%20by%20YouTube%20on%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EContent%20containing%20hurtful%20and%20negative%20personal%20comments%2Fvideos%20about%20another%20person%20is%20not%20allowed%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EContent%20that%20incites%20others%20to%20harass%20or%20threaten%20individuals%20on%20or%20off%20YouTube%20is%20not%20allowed%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20video%20was%20uploaded%2C%20the%20three%20celebrities%20who%20were%20named%20(Romila%20Thapar%2C%20Professor%20Irfan%20Habib%20and%20Barkha%20Dutt)%20started%20facing%20various%20threats%20and%20humiliation%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20viewers%20of%20the%20video%20abused%20and%20trolled%20them%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20leave%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20not%20only%20harmful%20to%20their%20mental%20health%20and%20safety%2C%20but%20also%20to%20democracy%20and%20public%20discourse%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHate%20Speech%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20This%20podcast%20incites%20hatred%20towards%20Muslims%20and%20other%20religious%20groups%20by%20making%20defamatory%20and%20misleading%20claims%20about%20their%20beliefs%2C%20practices%2C%20history%20and%20intentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExamples%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%2029%3A05%20mark%2C%20J.%20Sai%20Deepak%20states%20that%20India%20will%20be%20safe%20only%20when%20there%20is%20a%20Hindu%20majority.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20according%20to%20him%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20population%20of%20other%20religions%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%2029%3A50%20mark%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20the%20Muslim%20population%20is%20rising%20in%20areas%20which%20are%20actively%20%E2%80%98fighting%20for%20Pakistan%E2%80%99.%20His%20implied%20claim%20that%20Muslims%20are%20plotting%20to%20fight%20for%20Pakistan%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20population%20growth%20is%20not%20only%20a%20distortion%20of%20facts%20but%20a%20baseless%20and%20inflammatory%20allegation.%20The%20podcast%20specifically%20targets%20and%20disparages%20individuals%20or%20groups%20based%20on%20their%20identity%2C%20beliefs%20or%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%2030%3A56%20mark%2C%20Deepak%20claims%20that%20Indian%20Islam%20is%20a%20mythical%20creature%20that%20insults%20and%20defames%20a%20vast%20group%20of%20people%20and%20their%20faith%2C%20and%20questions%20the%20very%20basis%20of%20the%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%2031%3A52%20mark%2C%20he%20states%20that%20Indian%20Islam%20is%20an%20imposed%20faith%2C%20and%20most%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20converts.%20This%20is%20a%20derogatory%20comment%20for%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20any%20religion%2C%20which%20can%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20and%20religious%20beliefs%20of%20many%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%2028%3A16%20mark%2C%20he%20talks%20about%20a%20conspiracy%20theory%20that%20claims%20Hindu%20and%20Christian%20girls%20are%20being%20%E2%80%98sexually%20groomed%E2%80%99%20in%20Kerala.%20He%20also%20talks%20about%20%E2%80%98rate%20cards%E2%80%99%20mentioning%20the%20prices%20of%20girls.%20However%2C%20he%20does%20not%20cite%20any%20concrete%20sources%20for%20these%20claims%20which%20directly%20target%20Muslims.%20The%20entire%20discussion%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20video%20stems%20from%20a%20question%20about%20the%20future%20of%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20in%20India.%20The%20guest%20begins%20by%20stating%20that%20Christians%20in%20Kerala%20have%20realized%20that%20their%20security%20lies%20in%20having%20a%20significant%20Hindu%20population%20around%20them.%20To%20say%20so%20was%2C%20once%20again%2C%20an%20indirect%20attempt%20to%20demonize%20the%20Muslims%20who%20have%20a%20significant%20presence%20in%20Kerala%2C%20the%20southernmost%20state%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFake%20news%20and%20misinformation%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20At%20the%2018%3A18%20mark%2C%20he%20gives%20misleading%20information%20about%20an%20incident%20related%20to%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20protests%20of%202021.%20He%20claims%20that%20on%20January%2026%2C%202021%2C%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20the%20demonstrators%20pulled%20down%20the%20Indian%20national%20flag.%20This%20is%20a%20false%20claim%20which%20was%20debunked%20by%20various%20fact-checking%20platforms%20at%20the%20time.%20Several%20fact-checking%20organisations%20which%20are%20signatories%20to%20the%20International%20Fact-Checking%20Network%20(IFCN)%20also%20fact-checked%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20in%202022%2C%20Google%20and%20YouTube%20partnered%20with%20non-profits%20working%20against%20misinformation%20to%20fund%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Global%20Fact%20Check%20Fund%20to%20support%20a%20network%20of%20fact-checking%20organisations%20operating%20across%2065%20countries.%20They%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Fgoogle-youtube-fact-checking-misinformation%5C%22%3E%2413.2%20million%20grant%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20International%20Fact-Checking%20Network%20(IFCN)%2C%20part%20of%20the%20for-profit%20media%20organisation%20Poynter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20links%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snopes.com%2Ffact-check%2Ffarmers-protest-india-flag%2F%5C%22%3Efirst%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthelogicalindian.com%2Ffact-check%2Ffarmers-protest-26422%5C%22%3Esecond%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boomlive.in%2Ffact-check%2Fkhalistan-flag-hoisted-at-red-fort-a-factcheck-11719%5C%22%3Ethird%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Ffarmers-protest-zee-news-falsely-claims-indian-flag-replaced-with-khalsa-flag-on-red-fort%2F%5C%22%3Efourth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fwebqoof%2Ftricolour-removed-from-red-fort-zee-news-claim-lacks-proof%5C%22%3Efifth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Ffarmers-protest-no-protestors-did-not-replace-tricolour-with-khalistan-flag-at-red-fort%2F%5C%22%3Esixth%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20screenshots%20from%20various%20fact-checking%20organisations%20that%20debunk%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20Indian%20flag%20was%20pulled%20down%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20on%20January%2026%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5