ade%20a%20mockery%20of%20my%20trauma%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESentence%20rocks%20hip-hop%20community%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20David%20Herriford%20said%20he%20received%20more%20than%2070%20letters%20on%20Lanez%E2%80%99s%20behalf%2C%20including%20from%20his%20celebrity%20friends%20like%20Australian%20rapper%20Iggy%20Azalea%2C%20who%20he%20said%20had%20requested%20a%20sentence%20that%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctransformational%2C%20not%20life-destroying%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELanez%20asked%20the%20judge%20for%20leniency%2C%20saying%20he%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20what%20he%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20could%20turn%20back%20the%20series%20of%20events%20that%20night%20and%20change%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20would%2C%20Lanez%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20victim%20was%20my%20friend.%20The%20victim%20is%20someone%20I%20still%20care%20for%20to%20this%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHerriford%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdifficult%20to%20reconcile%E2%80%9D%20the%20kind%20person%20and%20good%20father%20many%20people%20described%20Lanez%20as%20being%20during%20the%20hearing%20with%20the%20person%20who%20fired%20the%20gun%20at%20Megan%20Thee%20Stallion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sentence%20brings%20to%20an%20end%20a%20dramatic%20dispute%20in%20the%20hip-hop%20community%20that%20cast%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20reluctance%20of%20Black%20victims%20to%20speak%20to%20police%2C%20gender%20politics%20in%20hip-hop%2C%20online%20toxicity%2C%20and%20calls%20to%20better%20protect%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmaya-angelou-becomes-first-black-woman-to-appear-on-us-coin%2Fa-60390286%5C%22%3EBlack%20women%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELos%20Angeles%20County%20District%20Attorney%20George%20Gascon%20said%2C%20after%20December%E2%80%99s%20verdict%2C%20that%20women%2C%20especially%20Black%20women%2C%20are%20often%20afraid%20to%20report%20crimes%20such%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http