%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20is%20concerned%20over%20a%20Union%20government%20plan%20to%20bring%20libraries%20across%20the%20country%20under%20the%20Concurrent%20List%20%E2%80%93%20or%20List%20III%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20Many%20in%20the%20state%20view%20the%20move%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20agenda%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20libraries%20and%20spread%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20regulate%20funds%20and%20grants%20from%20national%20institutions%20like%20Rajaram%20Mohan%20Roy%20Library%20Foundation%20to%20state%20councils%20of%20libraries%20and%20individual%20libraries%2C%E2%80%9D%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kerala%20Library%20Council%2C%20V.K.%20Madhu%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20is%20likely%20to%20introduce%20a%20Bill%20in%20parliament%20to%20bring%20libraries%20under%20the%20Concurrent%20List%2C%20where%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20states%20have%20equal%20jurisdiction.%20Education%20is%20already%20under%20the%20Concurrent%20List.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20such%20a%20law%20is%20enacted%2C%20we%20will%20be%20compelled%20to%20buy%20books%20spreading%20Sangh%20Parivar%E2%80%99s%20ideology%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madhu%20further%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBooks%20on%20scientific%20thought%20and%20rational%20thinking%20would%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20priority%20list.%20Regressive%20books%20would%20replace%20them%2C%20and%20the%20future%20generations%20would%20suffer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%E2%80%99s%20higher%20education%20minister%20R.%20Bindu%20said%20the%20move%20was%20aimed%20at%20usurping%20control%20of%20knowledge%20dissemination%20and%20routing%20regressive%20ideas%20through%20the%20library%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20secular%2C%20progressive%2C%20and%20inclusive%20library%20system%20in%20Kerala%20that%20has%20evolved%20over%20the%20years%20as%20a%20global%20model.%20Libraries%20are%20a%20state%20matter%2C%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20interference%20must%20be%20resisted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFirst%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20better%20for%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20tell%20other%20states%20to%20emulate%20the%20Kerala%20library%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20Indian%20states%2C%20only%20Kerala%20has%20accorded%20autonomous%20status%20to%20libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2046%2C746%20registered%20public%20libraries%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Kerala%20tops%20the%20list%20with%209%2C515.%20Along%20with%20libraries%20of%20educational%20institutions%2C%20the%20state%20has%20an%20estimated%2014%2C000%20libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFood%20for%20thought%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Ajay%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20the%20director-general%20of%20the%20Kolkata-based%20Raja%20Rammohun%20Roy%20Library%20Foundation%2C%20revealed%20at%20the%20recently%20held%20Festival%20of%20Libraries%202023%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20was%20planning%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20the%20conclave%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20lauded%20the%20organisers%3A%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20efforts%20will%20spread%20awareness%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20youth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.V.K.%20Panayal%2C%20one%20of%20the%2023%20representatives%20of%20the%20Kerala%20State%20Library%20Council%20who%20attended%20the%20Festival%20of%20Libraries%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3ESouth%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFirst%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20a%20draft%20legislation%20was%20discussed%20at%20the%20delegate%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Panayal%2C%20Professor%20Singh%20wanted%20state%20governments%20to%20adopt%20resolutions%20backing%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20bring%20libraries%20under%20the%20Concurrent%20List.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELibraries%20are%20now%20a%20state%20subject%2C%20meaning%20states%20have%20control%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20had%20witnessed%20a%20strong%20library%20movement%2C%20a%20unique%20public%20library%20system%2C%20which%20witnessed%20the%20mushrooming%20of%20libraries%20and%20reading%20rooms%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20movement%20significantly%20contributed%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20high%20literary%20status%2C%20besides%20inculcating%20the%20reading%20habit%20in%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20now%20observes%20June%2019%2C%20the%20death%20anniversary%20of%20P.N.%20Panicker%2C%20who%20spearheaded%20the%20movement%2C%20as%20Reading%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWay%20of%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20Library%20Council%20member%20Managalath%20Chandran%20said%20the%20state%20would%20resist%20any%20legislation%20to%20bring%20libraries%20under%20the%20Concurrent%20List.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-300x200.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Small%20libraries%20and%20reading%20rooms%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20Kerala.%20(File%20photo%2FSouth%20First)%5C%22%20data-srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-750x499.jpg%20750w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary.jpg%20960w%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-750x499.jpg%20750w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary.jpg%20960w%5C%22%20data-pin-no-hover%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FFortKochiLibrary-300x200.jpg%5C%22%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%20100vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%20data-sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%20100vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-127698%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22392%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESmall%20libraries%20and%20reading%20rooms%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20Kerala.%20Photo%3A%20South%20First%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhu%20said%20Kerala%20has%20a%20robust%20tradition%20of%20libraries%20that%20has%20been%20in%20existence%20for%20centuries.%20In%201827%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20public%20libraries%20was%20set%20up%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram.%20It%20now%20functions%20as%20the%20Central%20State%20Library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Kerala%2C%20libraries%20are%20a%20way%20of%20life.%20They%20helped%20spread%20progressive%20politics%20as%20well%20as%20popular%20science%20movements.%20Libraries%20are%20competing%20with%20each%20other%20to%20organise%20mega%20literary%20events%20and%20social%20gatherings%2C%20other%20than%20lending%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cheeral%2C%20Wayanad%2C%20resident%20M%20Govindan%2C%20who%20divides%20his%20spare%20time%20between%20the%20local%20library%20and%20activities%20of%20Kerala%20Sastra%20Sahitya%20Parishad%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFirst%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Malabar%20region%2C%20the%20library%20movement%20evolved%20as%20part%20of%20the%20nationalist%20movement%2C%20mainly%20thanks%20to%20the%20Leftists.%20Marxist%20thinker%20K%20Damodaran%20was%20one%20of%20the%20pioneering%20leaders%20who%20tried%20to%20build%20a%20network%20of%20these%20libraries%20and%20make%20them%20part%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2014%2C%201937%2C%20the%20Malabar%20Grandhashala%20Sangham%20(a%20library%20collective)%20was%20formed%20to%20coordinate%20the%20library%20movement%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20we%20undertake%20many%20activities%20besides%20lending%20books%20to%20attract%20people.%20Most%20cultural%20events%20in%20Kerala%20are%20being%20held%20by%20libraries%2C%E2%80%9D%20M.P.%20Jayan%2C%20a%20library%20activist%20from%20Kannur%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Mayyil%20model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20libraries%20have%20become%20integral%20to%20Kerala%20society.%20People%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKandoth%20Santha%20of%20Mayyil%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Kannur%20district%2C%20was%20one%20among%20them.%20A%20voracious%20reader%20from%20a%20poor%20family%2C%20she%20willed%20her%20life%20savings%20to%20the%20local%20Navakerala%20Library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20death%20due%20to%20COVID-19%2C%20her%20sons%20Unnikrishnan%20and%20Vinod%20Kumar%20spent%20their%20mother%E2%80%99s%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20savings%20to%20renovate%20the%20library.%20It%20now%20sports%20a%20new%20upper%20floor.%20Spread%20over%2034%20sq%20km%2C%20the%20Mayyil%20Grama%20Panchayat%20has%2014%20full-fledged%20libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202020%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20declared%20Mayyil%20Grama%20Panchayat%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20panchayat%20with%20a%20digitised%20library%20network%2C%20which%20could%20be%20accessed%20from%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20during%20the%20pandemic-endorsed%20lockdown%20that%20we%20thought%20of%20digitising%20all%20our%20libraries%20apart%20from%20bringing%20them%20under%20one%20network.%20The%20coronavirus%20prevented%20people%20from%20visiting%20libraries%20and%20selecting%20books.%20Those%20confined%20to%20houses%20had%20no%20other%20hobby%20to%20kill%20time%20other%20than%20reading%20books.%20So%20we%20evolved%20this%20concept%20of%20networking%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20social%20activist%20U.%20Janardhanan%2C%20who%20initiated%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CE-books%20are%20not%20affordable%20to%20most%20people.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20give%20digital%20versions%20of%20all%20books%20in%20our%20libraries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFirst%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20libraries%20have%20books%20in%20Malayalam%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20English.%20A%20total%20of%202%2C09%2C404%20books%20are%20available%20online%20from%20Mayyil.%20Local%20MLA%20James%20Mathew%20sanctioned%20money%20to%20buy%20computers%20and%20other%20facilities%20for%20the%20project%20from%20his%20local%20area%20development%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarnataka%2C%20too%2C%20is%20worried%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20has%206%2C890%20registered%20libraries.%20They%20include%205%2C766%20gram%20panchayat%20libraries%2C%20127%20nomad%20libraries%2C%20and%20seven%20children%E2%80%99s%20libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepartment%20of%20Public%20Libraries%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Administrative%20Officer%20Manu%20M%20said%20he%20had%20not%20come%20across%20any%20Bill%20envisaging%20bringing%20libraries%20under%20the%20Concurrent%20List.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20neither%20received%20any%20order%20nor%20notification%20related%20to%20this%20Bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFirst%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKarnataka%20is%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20pass%20the%20Karnataka%20Public%20Libraries%20Act%2C%201965.%20Later%2C%20around%2020%20states%20introduced%20similar%20bills%2C%E2%80%9D%20Karnataka%20State%20Library%20Association%20President%20Dr%20M%20Krishnamurthy%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFirst.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20have%20information%20about%20this%20Bill.%20However%2C%20the%20state%20libraries%20must%20be%20under%20state%20jurisdiction.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20City%20Central%20Library%20is%20entitled%20to%20get%20around%20Rs%206%20crore%20annually%20from%20the%20BBMP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20Union%20government%20takes%20libraries%20under%20its%20control%2C%20then%20the%20question%20is%20how%20will%20the%20libraries%20get%20that%20fund%20because%20the%20central%20library%20will%20come%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Culture.%20We%20will%20have%20detailed%20information%20about%20its%20implications%20only%20when%20the%20Bill%20is%20introduced%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELibrary%20movement%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20has%20around%202%2C506%20libraries%2C%20including%20branch%20libraries%2C%20government%2C%20and%20book%20deposit%20centres%20that%20are%20run%20by%20Zilla%20Grandhalaya%20Samsthas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20libraries%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20are%20managed%20by%20municipal%20corporations%2C%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20cooperative%20societies%2C%20and%20voluntary%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20undivided%20state%20was%20formed%20in%201956%2C%20the%20Madras%20Public%20Libraries%20Act%20was%20in%20operation%20in%20the%2011%20districts%20of%20the%20Andhra%20region%2C%20and%20the%20Hyderabad%20Public%20Libraries%20Act%20was%20in%20force%20in%20the%20nine%20districts%20in%20the%20Telangana%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20have%20a%20composite%20Act%2C%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Public%20Libraries%20Act%20was%20enacted%20in%201960.%20This%20Act%20was%20amended%20successively%20in%201964%2C%201969%2C%201987%2C%201989%2C%20and%20in%202016.%20After%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20separate%20Act%20for%20Telangana%20libraries%20was%20enacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20library%20movement%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%20that%20spread%20across%20all%20regions.%20The%20success%20of%20the%20public%20library%20movement%20in%20Andhra%20could%20be%20traced%20to%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%2019th%20century.%20It%20grew%20steadily%20in%20the%20subsequent%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201800%2C%20a%20private%20library%20belonging%20to%20the%20Paravasthu%20family%20was%20opened%20to%20the%20public.%20It%20was%20subsequently%20developed%20as%20Arsha%20Grandhalaya.%20Raja%20Rameshwar%20Rayalu%E2%80%99s%20(1821-1865)%20library%20was%20also%20opened%20to%20the%20public%20at%20Wanaparthy%20and%20Mahabubnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20has%204%2C641%20libraries%20under%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Public%20Libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20Libraries%20were%20opened%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20as%20per%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Public%20Libraries%20Act%2C%20of%201948.%20The%20Directorate%20of%20Public%20Libraries%20was%20formed%20in%201972%20to%20improve%20the%20library%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%204%2C641%20libraries%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20also%20has%20libraries%20at%20hospitals%2C%20prisons%2C%20and%20passport%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fkarnataka%2Funion-government-looks-to-move-libraries-from-state-to-concurrent-list-kerala-karnataka-flag-concerns%2F%5C%22%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-unique%3D%5C%22jnews_module_127562_0_64d332b968c50%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691573449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09131250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-09-at-1.11.59.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fconcern-as-union-govt-mulls-moving-libraries-from-state-to-concurrent-list%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala%20and%20Karnataka%20have%20expressed%20worry%20that%20the%20move%20aims%20to%20usurp%20control%20of%20knowledge%20dissemination%20and%20could%20be%20used%20to%20spread%20regressive%20ideas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fconcern-as-union-govt-mulls-moving-libraries-from-state-to-concurrent-list%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Larsen%20%26%20Toubro%20planning%20to%20invest%20as%20much%20as%20%2412%20bn%20over%20next%20five%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691570055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-06%2F13%2Ffull%2F1686645718-7795.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flarsen-toubro-planning-to-invest-as-much-as-12-bn-over-next-five-years-123080900284_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22L%26amp%3BT%20Energy%20Green%20Tech%2C%20a%20unit%20of%20the%20conglomerate%2C%20will%20execute%20the%20clean%20energy%20strategy%20and%20over%20time%20may%20expand%20into%20fuel%20cells%2C%20grid%20batteries%20and%20hydrogen%20vending%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flarsen-toubro-planning-to-