iti1-1691406583-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326467%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMypalclub%20employees%20with%20their%20mobile%20medical%20unit%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%20we%20treated%20the%20animals%20and%20got%20them%20adopted.%20We%20helped%203%2C000%20animals%20find%20homes.%20As%20we%20grew%2C%20we%20started%20doing%20more%20rescue%20work%20and%20were%20joined%20by%20veterinary%20doctors.%20What%20I%20found%20was%20that%20the%20animals%20suffered%20a%20lot%20when%20they%20were%20being%20transported%20for%20treatment.%20They%20were%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20stress%20and%20many%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it.%20I%20realised%20that%20it%20would%20be%20better%20if%20they%20were%20treated%20at%20their%20location%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298187%2Fbihar-snake-man-fights-superstition-to-rescue-snakes-sets-up-animal-centre%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20field%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20started%20operating%20mobile%20medical%20units%20in%202017.%20The%20ambulances%20are%20equipped%20with%20emergency%20oxygen%20and%20medical%20facilities%20to%20provide%20on-the-spot%20treatment.%20Aditi%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20para%20veterinary%20worker%2C%20driver%20and%20handler%20in%20each%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20treating%20the%20animal%20on%20the%20field%2C%20we%20involve%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20particular%20area.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20when%20the%20community%20gets%20involved%20that%20the%20animal%20stands%20a%20chance%20of%20living%20a%20better%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aditi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20work%20is%20not%20over%20after%20treating%20the%20animal%20on%20day%20one.%20We%20follow%20up%20daily%20till%20the%20animal%2