e-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326203%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMadhusmita%20is%20joined%20by%20Smita%2C%20Swagatika%2C%20and%20Snehanjali%20in%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20women%20were%20called%20to%20help%20the%20administration%20in%20transporting%20the%20injured%20to%20the%20hospitals%20and%20cremating%20unidentified%20and%20unclaimed%20bodies.%20%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20situation%2C%20we%20first%20focussed%20on%20admitting%20severely%20injured%20people%20to%20hospitals%20in%20Cuttack%20and%20Balasore.%20Later%2C%20we%20were%20permitted%20to%20cremate%20five%20bodies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20many%20as%2029%20bodies%20are%20still%20preserved%20in%20AIIMS%2C%20Bhubaneswar%20premises%20to%20be%20identified%20by%20the%20authorities.%20After%20receiving%20the%20final%20round%20of%20DNA%20cross-matching%20reports%2C%20the%20authorities%20may%20conduct%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126580%2Fcremation-wood-green-alternatives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emass%20cremation%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20unidentified%20bodies.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20is%20ongoing%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20identification%20of%20the%20dead.%20We%20might%20soon%20be%20called%20to%20cremate%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECourage%20above%20all%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20Madhusmita%20was%20working%20with%20a%20Kolkata%20hospital%20as%20a%20nurse%20in%20the%20paediatrics%20department.%20Over%20her%2015%20year%20career%2C%20she%20often%20saw%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20see%20wailing%20children%20and%20elderly%20next%20to%20their%20loved%20ones.%20They%20would%20not%20have%20sufficient%20money%20to%20perform%20the%20last%20rites%20and%20the%20authorities%20demanded%20a%20huge%20amount%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remembered%20how%20my%20husband%20%5Bwho%20lived%20back%20home%20in%20Odisha%5D%20would%20do%20this%20work%20without%20charging%20any%20amount.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20when%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20leg%20was%20fractured%20after%20slipping%20on%20a%20railway%20track%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20come%20back%20to%20her%20hometown.%20When%20no%20one%20from%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20non-profit%20Pradeep%20Sewa%20Trust%20was%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20job%20of%20cremating%20bodies%2C%20she%20stepped%20in%20and%20quit%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20receiving%20information%20from%20the%20GRP%2C%20Madhusmita%20drives%20to%20the%20spot%2C%20from%20where%20they%20lift%20the%20bodies.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2