s%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20migrate%20to%20urban%20areas%20in%20search%20of%20livelihood%20opportunities.%20While%20they%20find%20new%20jobs%20and%20homes%2C%20what%20happens%20to%20their%20children%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBengaluru-based%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENomita%20Sikand%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20families%20settle%20in%20the%20urban%20spaces%20for%20labour%20jobs.%20And%20in%20the%20bargain%2C%20children%20are%20not%20a%20concern%20or%20focus.%20They%20miss%20out%20on%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20the%20children%20are%20enrolled%20in%20government%20schools%2C%20they%20hardly%20understand%20anything%20as%20schools%20are%20in%20Kannada%20%5Bor%20another%20regional%20language%5D%20medium.%20So%20eventually%2C%20they%20stop%20going%20to%20school.%20Also%2C%20typically%2C%20children%20are%20enrolled%20in%20age-appropriate%20classes%2C%20but%20their%20learning%20level%20might%20not%20be%20at%20that%20grade%20because%20of%20irregular%20continuity%20in%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20by%20a%20common%20purpose%2C%20Nomita%20along%20with%20Bengaluru-based%20Rizwan%20Ahmed%2C%20Manimakalai%20Raja%2C%20Preethy%20Rao%20Patel%2C%20Joseph%20Deyone%20Jacobi%2C%20and%20Somya%20Nand%20came%20together%20to%20mainstream%20such%20children%20into%20the%20government%20schools%20and%20public%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-2-1690981282.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sextet%20co-founded%20Gubbachi%20to%20educate%20migrant%20children.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-2-1690981282.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-2-1690981282-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-2-1690981282-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-2-1690981282-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-2-1690981282-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326086%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20sextet%20co-founded%20Gubbachi%20to%20educate%20migrant%20children.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20sextet%20co-founded%20%E2%80%98Gubbachi%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Karnataka-based%20non-profit%20that%20works%20towards%20the%20educational%20inclusion%20of%20out-of-school%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F101749%2Ffound-joy-teaching-migrant-school-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarginalised%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20migrant%20families.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20implement%20an%20approach%20to%20get%20a%20child%20mainstreamed%2C%20and%20subsequently%2C%20their%20family%20with%20them%2C%20so%20that%20they%20feel%20how%20a%20citizen%20should%20feel%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2053-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMulti-level%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20their%20higher%20education%20at%20Azim%20Premji%20University%20and%20doing%20internships%2C%20they%20observed%20the%20dire%20educational%20state%20of%20migrant%20children.%20To%20address%20these%20gaps%20in%20educational%20exclusion%2C%20Gubbachi%20mainstreams%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F241795%2Fbengaluru-sub-inspector-teaches-migrant-labourers-students-classes-free-education-police-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3