m%3Eto%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20their%20dreams.%20In%202018%2C%20they%20started%20Dabba%20Drop%2C%20and%20Anshu%20says%20that%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20starting%20an%20eco-friendly%20delivery%20business%20was%20the%20waste%20that%20gets%20accumulated%20when%20we%20order%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20people%20have%20started%20ordering%20a%20lot%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20arrival%20of%20food%20delivery%20apps.%20After%20having%20that%20food%2C%20we%20end%20up%20with%20a%20bin%20full%20of%20plastic.%20The%20packaging%20is%20very%20wasteful%20and%20greasy.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20recycle%20it.%20So%20I%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20better%20way%20to%20order%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anshu%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Mumbai%20with%20a%20Tamilian%20mother%20and%20Punjabi%20father%2C%20food%20was%20a%20big%20part%20of%20her%20life%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20my%20favourite%20food%20when%20we%20would%20go%20out%20to%20eat%20was%20%3Cem%3Epav%20bhaji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20chinese.%20When%20I%E2%80%99d%20get%20home%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20try%20to%20recreate%20those%20dishes.%20This%20way%20I%20could%20continue%20to%20taste%20the%20flavours.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20childhood%20in%20Mumbai%20meant%20that%20Anshu%20was%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabbawalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20have%20been%20serving%20food%20to%20over%202%20lakh%20people%20daily%20since%201890.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20mix%20of%20love%20for%20home-cooked%20food%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabbawala%20institution%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20led%20her%20to%20quit%20her%2015-year-long%20career%20as%20a%20TV%20producer%20in%20East%20London%20to%20start%20Dabba%20Drop%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20theatre%20of%20the%20humble%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Edabba%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20menu%20of%20the%20dabba%20changes%20weekly%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326057%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20dishes%20in%20the%20dabba%20are%20Anshu%E2%80%99s%20ode%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20cuisines%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202018%2C%20Anshu%20texted%20a%20few%20friends%20about%20her%20idea%20and%20asked%20if%20anyone%20would%20be%20interested%20in%20her%20home-cooked%20%3Cem%3Edabbas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20cooked%20for%20five%20people%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20trial%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20entrepreneur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remembers%20the%20first%20evening%20as%20though%20it%20were%20yesterday.%20She%20had%20cooked%20a%20meal%20consisting%20of%20a%20pumpkin%20%3Cem%3Eerrisery%20%3C%2Fem%3E(curry)%2C%20green%20beans%20and%20peas%20%3Cem%3Eporiyal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(vegetable%20dish)%2C%20cabbage%20%3Cem%3Ethoran%20%3C%2Fem%3E(vegetable%20dish%20with%20coconut)%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20%3Cem%3Epuliohare%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tamarind%20rice)%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3